  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-SET-61255 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101129"> Verification Test Cases </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 04:30:28 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 04:30:28 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Set Key:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VERTC</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302095</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-SET-61255</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verification Test Cases</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description (Describe what the element set is trying to accomplish) :</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>RAASIC (Fill out the RAASIC table below):</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>The following RAASIC table is used to understand who needs to be involved in the lifecycle of the elements within this section.</p>
       <ul>
        <li>Enter all the Roles expected to participate in each of the categories.</li>
        <li>Approvers: It is expected that one or more personnel within the group listed&nbsp;is required to participate in the review process.</li>
        <li>Enter 'N/A' for fields deemed unnecessary.</li>
       </ul> <p><span style=3D"color:#e74c3c">&lt;Example of roles: Project Manager, Development Manager, Product Manager, Embedded, Safety, Mechanical, Electrical, Documentation, Training, GNC, ESO, PMO, PAT, Senior Leadership, Tech Lead, Support, Supply Chain, HR, Facilities, Director, VP, Customers, Stakeholders,&nbsp;etc.&gt;</span></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>
       <table border=3D"1" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" style=3D"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%">
        <thead>
         <tr>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Responsible</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) expected to&nbsp;work&nbsp;on the task.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Accountable</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) accountable for getting the task&nbsp;completed. They give the final approval and&nbsp;acts as a decision maker.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Approvers</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) accountable to&nbsp;ensure the task is completed&nbsp;to an acceptable level.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Support</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) helps the ones&nbsp;responsible and could actively work on the task.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Informed</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) requires&nbsp;information on the status, any decisions being made, and when the task is complete.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Consulted</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) offers&nbsp;advice or guidance&nbsp;but are not actively working on the task.</span></p></th>
         </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
         <tr>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
         </tr>
        </tbody>
       </table> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-940 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101178"> Mower to not stop for grass trimmings </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 04:47:12 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">12/02/2025 06:34:28 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-940</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302097</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower to not stop for grass trimmings</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Approved</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>When a mower mows very thick or long grass, the mowed grass clippings can be thrown where the LiDAR can "see" the grass clippings. The mower must not stop for grass clippings</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Subsystem test (VAI)</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A fairway is available to mow that has long grass</li>
        <li>The fairway has been mapped and has a plan in Mobius</li>
        <li>The fairway is free from all obstacles that may stop the mower</li>
        <li><strong>The group of thrown grass clippings needs to be larger than 6 inches across and 1 foot long</strong></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 3.7</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A fairway that has long grass</li>
        <li>The fairway with long grass has been mapped</li>
        <li>The mapped fairway has a plan associated with the fairway in Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>In the field/on a golf course</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A real mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Manually move the mower to the fairway with long grass, assign the mower to yourself in Mobius, and load a plan for the fairway&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, When the mower is moved to the fairway, assigned to you, and a plan loaded, the mower will be ready for the test to start<br>2: Start the mower on the fairway with long grass using the loaded plan, While the mower is mowing long grass, grass clippings will be thrown in front of the mower<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Allow the mower to complete the plan on the fairway&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, The mower shall not stop at any time due to grass clippings getting thrown in front of the mower</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-942 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101190"> Screen Data is not lost when phone is locked and unlocked after five minutes </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 04:56:05 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 04:56:05 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-942</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302099</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Screen Data is not lost when phone is locked and unlocked after five minutes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Clearly describe what the test aims to verify or validate.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Specify the boundaries of the test (e.g., subsystem, complete system).</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>User is logged into MOBIUS Mobile Application</li>
        <li>User has opened to the error report screen</li>
        <li>User has entered data into the Title and Description fields</li>
        <li>User has locked the phone</li>
        <li>At Least Five minutes have passed</li>
        <li>JWT Token has not expired</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Detail the required system state or setup before testing begins.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Test both with and without cell signal</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">List all tools, instruments, and simulators used during testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Unlock phone</li>
        <li>Open MOBIUS Mobile Application</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Log into Mobius mobile application, User is logged into Mobius mobile application<br>2: Navigate to the error report screen and type "Test" in the Title and Description fields, Data will be entered<br>3: Lock phone, Phone locks<br>4: Wait more than 5 minutes<br>5: Unlock phone, Mobius mobile application will open directly to the error report page and User will see "Test" in both Title and Description fields</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestComplete</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FFFF66" width=3D"80%">Medium</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-943 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101213"> Verify SMU requires WAT on the required frequency </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:18:14 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/12/2026 07:51:58 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-943</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302106</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify SMU requires WAT on the required frequency</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>The SMU requires WAT before automated operation can begin on a predefined frequency</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Given an SMU in specification and the SMU is powered on</p> <p>When the timeframe between the last execution of the WAT expires</p> <p>Then the SMU will send an alert to require a new execution of the WAT before autonomous running can continue</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Specify the boundaries of the test (e.g., subsystem, complete system).</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Note any assumptions made prior to testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Detail the required system state or setup before testing begins.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Include hardware/software configurations, test benches, or simulation tools.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">List all tools, instruments, and simulators used during testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: After executing a Walk Around Test user waits 24 hours and attempts to operate the mower autonomously, User will be required and informed by an alert to perform a Walk Around Test before the SMU will allow autonomous running</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
