  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-955 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5103090"> Up/Down Prioritization Part 1 </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/17/2025 05:36:59 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/17/2025 05:36:59 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-955</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3303332</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Up/Down Prioritization Part 1</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>The mower should start driving with reels down, then lift completely, then immediately drops</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Specify the boundaries of the test (e.g., subsystem, complete system).</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Note any assumptions made prior to testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop</li>
        <li>Mobius Preston Dev Server</li>
        <li>Physical Mower with all reels unplugged</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Preston Dev Server with the test fairway and the UpDnConflict plan</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">List all tools, instruments, and simulators used during testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: User unplugs the reels for the mower and navigates to Settings/[Mower]/VCU configuration and sets the MowerDtc.errorDisable to 1, then sets the reels.actionBuffer.durationDropMsec to 950 and the reels.actionBuffer.durationLiftMsec to 1150, The DKS values should change successfully<br>2: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Load the UpDnconflict plan for the test fairway in preston then execute the plan&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, The mower will start driving with the reels up, then down, then completely lift, then immediately drop</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
