  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-965 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5103300"> Adjusted from Feedback (Completed Example) Template Drop in From TestCase LFWM-VALTC-461 </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/17/2025 06:35:27 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/17/2025 06:35:27 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-965</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3303527</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Adjusted from Feedback (Completed Example) Template Drop in From TestCase LFWM-VALTC-461</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Shared between Software and Hardware:<br> <br> (Actual Name)&nbsp;</strong>Verify the 1.1-meter hazard zone from mower body to hazard boundary (Autonomous Mode)</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scenario (BDD intent and required test data)</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p><em>Scenario:</em>&nbsp;Vehicle encounters an obstacle 1.1 m from the outermost fixed point of the mower (“mower body”) to the hazard boundary.</p></li>
        <li><p><em>Given</em>&nbsp;mower in Autonomous mode on approved test map</p></li>
        <li><p><em>When</em>&nbsp;an obstacle intrudes within the 1.1 m hazard boundary</p></li>
        <li><p><em>Then</em>&nbsp;mower executes Category 0 e-stop within ≤ 2.0 s, beacon and audible alarm assert, ActivityState =3D EStopped</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Preconditions &amp; Configurations</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mode: Autonomous enabled;</p></li>
        <li><p>Map/Plan loaded;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Expected Results</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mower executes Category 0 e-stop within ≤ 2.0 s, beacon and audible alarm assert, ActivityState =3D EStopped<br> &nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Hardware Specific:&nbsp;</strong><br> &nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Preconditions &amp; Configurations</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mode: wireless e-stop paired/healthy</p></li>
        <li><p>geofence active; no active faults</p></li>
        <li><p>Battery SOC ≥ 40%</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Environmental Conditions &amp; Infrastructure</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Test Plan Specific: Manual testing to visually verify mower lifted and lowered reels&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Test Resources</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Obstacles (two identical): 40×40×60 cm foam block with rigid core; reflectivity ~medium; ID tags OB-HZ-01, OB-HZ-02</p></li>
        <li><p>Tape Measure to measure Hazard boundary distance: 1.10 m ± 0.05 m from mower body reference</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Mitigations During Test:&nbsp;</strong>(Hardware specific)</p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Equipment (mower/obstacle): collision risk—<strong>Mitigation:</strong>&nbsp;foam obstacle; low approach speed; clear escape path.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>------//----------//-----------//-------------</p> <p>Drop-in Template</p>
       <ul>
        <li><strong>(Test Case Title Naming Convention:)&nbsp;</strong>Using the words Verify or Test, choose a short name for the test.</li>
        <li><strong>Scenario:</strong>&nbsp;(BDD Intent) High-level intention and required test data, expressed with (Given/When/Then | no how).</li>
        <li><strong>Preconditions &amp; Configurations:</strong>&nbsp;Hardware specific conditions to test ie.&nbsp;mode: map loaded; battery SOC, etc.</li>
        <li><strong>Environmental Conditions &amp; Infrastructure:</strong>&nbsp;Descriptor for the test plan</li>
        <li><strong>Test Resources:</strong>&nbsp;Physical items needed to test: Example mobile phone, foam blocks, tape measure</li>
        <li><strong>Expected Results:&nbsp;</strong>Description of behavior, timing, states</li>
        <li><strong>Mitigations During Test:</strong>&nbsp;Equipment specific, equipment&nbsp;motions, procedure for a catastrophic recovery</li>
       </ul> <p>*Use links to link to create traceability example: link(s) to other tests, automated test, test scripts, etc...</p> <p>**Use attachments to add artifacts that support the test such as screen shots, photos, example test data...</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Detail the required system state or setup before testing begins.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Include hardware/software configurations, test benches, or simulation tools.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">List all tools, instruments, and simulators used during testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Set up obstacle within the designated autonomous operating area of the mower&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;An obstacle is placed within the autonomous operating area of the mower&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>2: Create a path, or task, that intercepts the obstacle. Assign the mower to the path or task, The mower will be assigned a path or task to intercept the obstacle within the autonomous operating area.<br>3: Ensure the mower is in autonomous mode<br>4: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;The mower starts the path or task.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, As the mower approaches the obstacle, once the mower passes the 3 meter mark away from the obstacle, the mower will slow down<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;The mower approaches the obstacle&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;As the mower approaches the obstacle, once the mower hits the 1.1 meter mark away from the obstacle, the mower will stop at 1.1 meters.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>6: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;The mower is at 1.1 meters from the obstacle.&amp;nbsp;Use the second obstacle to trip the 1.1 meter hazard zone&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, The mower will immediately category 0 e-stop once the hazard zone has been tripped</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
