  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-972 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5160228"> Verify SMU stops mower when slope ≥ 25° </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">11/20/2025 08:00:57 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">11/20/2025 08:00:57 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-972</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3331879</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify SMU stops mower when slope ≥ 25°</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that when the mower enters a slope ≥ 25°, the SMU will stop the mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Tests slope detection and SMU safety response in both Software-in-the-Loop (SIL) and Hardware-in-the-Loop (HIL). Ensures that tipping hazards are mitigated by enforcing a stop before the slope exceeds 30°</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest "testable" SMU software version loaded</li>
        <li>Vehicle is operating in autonomous mode</li>
        <li>Map/path setup allows mower to reach ≥ 25° slope under test conditions</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mower is powered on and in autonomous mode</li>
        <li>Path with slope ≥ 25° is planned and loaded</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>RW mower on controlled slope course</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>RW mower on physical slope</li>
        <li>Mobius console open&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>​​​​​Diagnostic stop messages</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Start mower and toggle to autonomous mode<br>2: Command mower to drive a path that has a slope of 25° and reaches ≥ 30°, Mower will follow the path until it reaches ≥ 25°&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;the SMU will stop mower within (TBD) seconds&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;the SMU will stop mower before it reaches slope ≥ 30<br>3: Check Console Log, A log message will be sent that indicates slope detection and stop command</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
