  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1199 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5262193"> Audible alarm will sound when obstacle is detected in Warning Zone </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">01/07/2026 05:06:08 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/14/2026 06:08:15 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1199</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3395680</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Audible alarm will sound when obstacle is detected in Warning Zone</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>To validate the autonomous mower will sound an alarm when an obstacle is detected in the Warning Zone</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>VAI</li>
        <li>VCU</li>
        <li>LiDAR</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius is running</li>
        <li>A map is published on the Mobius server</li>
        <li>The map includes a drivable area fit to test in</li>
        <li>The mower is checked in to Mobius and operating normally</li>
        <li>The tester has access to an obstacle that does not pose a safety hazard</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 3.7</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map is published on the Mobius Server the mower is connected to</li>
        <li>The mower has been moved to the drivable area</li>
        <li>The tester has placed the obstacle that does not pose a safety risk in the drivable area</li>
        <li>The tester creates a plan (PTP, waypoint, mowing plan, path plan) that will intersect with&nbsp;the obstacle</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Real mower</li>
        <li>Real course</li>
        <li>Real obstacle</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A mower with an up to date VAI</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: While the mower is in Autonomous Mode, assign the mower to execute a plan that intersects the obstacle placed in the Preconditions., The mower shall execute the plan assigned to it.<br>2: While the mower is executing the plan, the obstacle will be within 5 meters of the mower.&amp;nbsp;, When the obstacle is within 5 meters of the mower in any direction, the VAI will communicate with the VCU, and the VCU will send a command to the sounders on the mower to start their Warning Zone pattern alarm.<br>3: Perform steps 1 and 2, but with the mower moving in reverse towards the obstacle.&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>In order to create a PTP/waypoint plan that forces the mower to drive in reverse, hold the Shift button on your keyboard and left click with the mouse behind the mower.&amp;nbsp;, When the obstacle is within 5 meters of the mower in any direction, the VAI will communicate with the VCU, and the VCU will send a command to the sounders on the mower to start their Warning Zone pattern alarm.<br>4: Perform steps 1 and 2, but with the mower driving past the obstacle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>Simply move the obstacle to one side or the other from the mower's desired path of travel.&amp;nbsp;, When the obstacle is within 5 meters of the mower in any direction, the VAI will communicate with the VCU, and the VCU will send a command to the sounders on the mower to start their Warning Zone pattern alarm.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1200 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5262217"> Audible alarm will sound when obstacle is detected in Hazard Zone </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">01/07/2026 05:25:37 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/14/2026 06:07:37 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1200</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3395701</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Audible alarm will sound when obstacle is detected in Hazard Zone</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>To validate the autonomous mower will sound an alarm when an obstacle is detected in the Hazard Zone</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>VAI</li>
        <li>VCU</li>
        <li>LiDAR</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius is running</li>
        <li>A map is published on the Mobius server</li>
        <li>The map includes a drivable area fit to test in</li>
        <li>The mower is checked in to Mobius and operating normally</li>
        <li>The tester has access to an obstacle that does not pose a safety hazard</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 3.7</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map is published on the Mobius Server the mower is connected to</li>
        <li>The mower has been moved to the drivable area</li>
        <li>The tester has placed the obstacle that does not pose a safety risk in the drivable area</li>
        <li>The tester creates a plan (PTP, waypoint, mowing plan, path plan) that will intersect with&nbsp;the obstacle</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Real mower</li>
        <li>Real course</li>
        <li>Real obstacle</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A mower with an up to date VAI</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: While the mower is in Autonomous Mode, assign the mower to execute a plan that intersects the obstacle placed in the Preconditions., The mower shall execute the plan assigned to it.<br>2: While the mower is executing the plan, the obstacle will be within 1.1 meters of the mower.&amp;nbsp;, When the obstacle is within 1.1 meters of the mower in any direction, the VAI will communicate with the VCU, and the VCU will send a command to the sounders on the mower to start their Warning Zone pattern alarm. The VAI will also raise a flag that there is an obstacle in the Hazard Zone. The VAI will send that flag to the VCU, the VCU will send an error to the user stating there is a Hazard Zone Violation.&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>The VCU will also kill the engine on the mower, but will keep the alarms active.<br>3: Perform steps 1 and 2, but with the mower moving in reverse towards the obstacle.&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>In order to create a PTP/waypoint plan that forces the mower to drive in reverse, hold the Shift button on your keyboard and left click with the mouse behind the mower.&amp;nbsp;, When the obstacle is within 1.1 meters of the mower in any direction, the VAI will communicate with the VCU, and the VCU will send a command to the sounders on the mower to start their Warning Zone pattern alarm. The VAI will also raise a flag that there is an obstacle in the Hazard Zone. The VAI will send that flag to the VCU, the VCU will send an error to the user stating there is a Hazard Zone Violation.&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>The VCU will also kill the engine on the mower, but will keep the alarms active.<br>4: Perform steps 1 and 2, but with the mower driving very close (within 1.1 meters) past the obstacle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>Simply move the obstacle to one side or the other from the mower's desired path of travel.&amp;nbsp;, When the obstacle is within 1.1 meters of the mower in any direction, the VAI will communicate with the VCU, and the VCU will send a command to the sounders on the mower to start their Warning Zone pattern alarm. The VAI will also raise a flag that there is an obstacle in the Hazard Zone. The VAI will send that flag to the VCU, the VCU will send an error to the user stating there is a Hazard Zone Violation.&lt;br /&gt;<br>&lt;br /&gt;<br>The VCU will also kill the engine on the mower, but will keep the alarms active.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FF0000" width=3D"80%">Critical / Safety</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1207 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5347829"> Jira ticket creation automation more than once a day </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/10/2026 08:23:22 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/17/2026 03:00:40 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1207</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3449648</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Jira ticket creation automation more than once a day</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Validate that Mobius Server will automatically populate the Customer Support Landscaping Jira space with Error Reports created on each instance of Mobius Server multiple times per day, per configuration settings.&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Error report creation is functional.</li>
        <li>Error reports are being created throughout the day.</li>
        <li>Jira Customer Support Landscaping space (CSL) is accessible.</li>
        <li>The default time set to automatically send error reports to Jira is set to 1:00pm and 12:00am local time.&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Additional Information</strong></p> <p>This is the location of the .json file to edit the times error reports are pulled into Jira:&nbsp;<span style=3D"color:#000000">C:\ASI\MobiusServer\ticketgenerator.appsettings.json</span></p> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius server up and running.&nbsp;</li>
        <li>An acceptable matching Mobius Desktop client.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Simulation.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server software.</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop client software.</li>
        <li>Jira login.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Error reports.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Step 1 needs to take place before 1:00pm local time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;With Mobius Server running, and logged in as any user, navigate to the Error Report creation window. Create an error report., An error report will be created and saved on the server.&amp;nbsp;, Error report creation screen can be found under the username in the top right corner of Mobius. Can be accessed at any point when running Mobius. Error report name does not matter.&amp;nbsp;<br>2: Wait for 1:00pm to pass. After 1:00pm has passed, navigate to the CSL Jira space., In the CSL Jira space, the test ticket created on the server will be present.&amp;nbsp;<br>3: While Mobius Server is running, and the error report created before 1:00pm has been automatically sent to Jira, navigate to the Error Report creation window. Create another error report., An error report will be created and saved on the server.&amp;nbsp;<br>4: Wait for 12:00am to pass. After 12:00am has passed, navigate to the CSL Jira space., In the CSL Jira space, the test ticket created on the server will be present.&amp;nbsp;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FFFF66" width=3D"80%">Medium</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1217 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5485243"> Verify mobius shall stop vehicle if off path error maximum is exceeded </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 11:04:22 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 11:04:22 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1217</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3477877</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify mobius shall stop vehicle if off path error maximum is exceeded</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that if the vehicle exceeds the defined off path error mobius shall stop the vehicle.&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client and Server</li>
        <li>VCU</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Note any assumptions made prior to testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius is running</li>
        <li>​​​​​​Vehicle is checked into mobius</li>
        <li>Map published with driveable area shape</li>
        <li>Vehicle located within driveable area shape</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>RW MOW</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">List all tools, instruments, and simulators used during testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Navigate to Settings &amp;gt; Vehicles (User assigned vehicle) &amp;gt; VCU configuration &amp;gt; Maximum Allowed Off Path Error, Maximum Allowed Off Path Error configuration is shown<br>2: Set Maximum Allowed Off Path Error to 0.1, Maximum Allowed Off Path Error adjusted to 0.1<br>3: In command mode, generate a waypoint and start vehicle on path with a sharp turn, Vehicle will stop when Maximum Allowed Off Path Error is exceeded<br>4: Revert Maximum Allowed Off Path Error to original value, Maximum Allowed Off Path Error adjusted to original value<br>5: Start vehicle along path again, Vehicle should complete path unless Maximum Allowed Off Path Error is exceeded again</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
