  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1216 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5459820"> Planning Can Toggle Mowing Approach </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/18/2026 08:04:07 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 08:30:56 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1216</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3462488</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Planning Can Toggle Mowing Approach</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>To validate the existence and function of a toggle switch in the Offline Planner that will allow, or disallow, the mowing of an approach</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
        <li>Mobius Server (planner)</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map has been created</li>
        <li>The map has a fairway that is plannable</li>
        <li>The Offline Planner can create a plan with an approach</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Future Release</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map has been created</li>
        <li>The map has a fairway that is plannable</li>
        <li>A sim, or real mower, is available to use for testing</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Simulation</li>
        <li>Real mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
        <li>A real or simulated mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A plan that is exported and included on the final Jira ticket that with the approach not mowed</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: With Mobius Server running, along with Mobius Desktop running, a map is published, and a fairway is located within the map with a DEFINED APPROACH, navigate to the Offline Planner, The user will be brought to the Offline Planner<br>2: Navigate through all testing steps until you are presented with the Mow Approach toggle&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Toggle the switch so it is in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;On&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;position&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Finish creating the plan, A plan will be created where a mowing swath(s) is created that passes over, and completes mowing, the approach<br>3: Create a new plan on the same fairway&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Navigate through all testing steps until you are presented with the Mow Approach toggle&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Toggle the switch so it is in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Off&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;position&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Finish creating the plan, A plan will be created where a mowing swath(s) is &lt;strong&gt;NOT &lt;/strong&gt;created and does &lt;strong&gt;not&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;pass over, and complete mowing, the approach</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
