  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-978 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5168636"> Planning Has Cleanup Lap </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/02/2025 06:48:19 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">12/02/2025 06:48:19 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-978</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3336738</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Planning Has Cleanup Lap</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>To validate that the Offline Planner in Mobius creates as many cleanup laps the user specifies.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Offline Planner.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server is running.</li>
        <li>A map with at least one fairway has been created and published.&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server is running either locally or on a test Azure server.</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop client version is being used and matches the version of Mobius Server being used.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Software</li>
        <li>Simulation</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: With Mobius Desktop Client open, and a map published that includes at least one fairway, navigate to the Offline Planner section of Mobius.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Walk through all steps in the Offline Planner using the default values., The Offline Planner will create a plan with&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;one&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;cleanup lap when using the default values.<br>2: Create a new plan using the same fairway. Walk through the Offline Planner steps until you reach the Boundary Lap Generation tab.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;On this tab, change the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Number of laps&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;to any value besides the default of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;1.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Finish creating the plan while keeping the number of cleanup laps dictated in the Boundary Lap Generation tab in mind., The Offline Planner will create a plan with the same number of cleanup laps dictated in the Boundary Lap Generation tab.<br>3: Create a new plan using the same fairway. Walk through the Offline Planner steps until you reach the Boundary Lap Generation tab again.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;This time, change the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Direction&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;to Clockwise.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Continue through the Offline Planner and finish creating the plan., The Offline Planner will create a plan with a cleanup lap in a Clockwise direction.<br>4: Create a new plan using the same fairway. Walk through the Offline Planner steps until you reach the Boundary Lap Generation tab again.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;This time, change the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Direction&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;to Counter Clockwise.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Continue through the Offline Planner and finish creating the plan., The Offline Planner will create a plan with a cleanup lap in a Counter Clockwise direction.<br>5: Create a new plan using the same fairway. Walk through the Offline Planner steps until you reach the Boundary Lap Generation tab.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;On this tab, change the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Number of laps&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;3&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;instead of the default of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;1.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Keep the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Order&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;set to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Inner First Outer Last&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Continue through the Offline Planner and finish creating the plan., The Offline Planner will create a plan with 3 cleanup laps. The order of cleanup laps will be set to complete the inner most cleanup lap first before the fairway interior has been mowed, and the outermost cleanup lap last, after the fairway has been mowed.<br>6: Create a new plan using the same fairway. Walk through the Offline Planner steps until you reach the Boundary Lap Generation tab.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;On this tab, change the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Number of laps&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;to any value besides the default of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;1.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Order&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Last&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Finish creating the plan while keeping the number of cleanup laps dictated in the Boundary Lap Generation tab in mind., The Offline Planner will create a plan with the same number of cleanup laps dictated during the plan creation. The cleanup laps will all be completed after the fairway interior has been mowed.<br>7: Create a new plan using the same fairway. Walk through the Offline Planner steps until you reach the Boundary Lap Generation tab.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;On this tab, change the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Number of laps&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;to any value besides the default of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;1.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Order&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;First&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Finish creating the plan while keeping the number of cleanup laps dictated in the Boundary Lap Generation tab in mind., The Offline Planner will create a plan with the same number of cleanup laps dictated during the plan creation. The cleanup laps will all be completed before the fairway interior has been mowed.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FFFF66" width=3D"80%">Medium</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1197 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5260535"> Verify Mobius does not crash when attempting to edit a plan </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">01/06/2026 03:48:47 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/07/2026 04:24:32 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1197</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3394563</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobius does not crash when attempting to edit a plan</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>This test aims to validate that a bug that was found during 3.7 release testing has been fixed. The bug was as described: When a user is running an installed build of Mobius Client, the client would crash when the user attempts to edit any plan.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop&nbsp;Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server is running</li>
        <li>There are multiple plans that have been created previously</li>
        <li>Those previously created plans are valid plans</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server is running</li>
        <li>A map has been published</li>
        <li>Plans have been created with that map with a different version of Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Software</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: With Mobius Desktop Client open, running, and actively connected to a Mobius Server, navigate to the Offline Planning section of Mobius.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;From the menu, select any plan and attempt to edit the plan by clicking on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Edit Plan&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;button.&amp;nbsp;, When the user attempts to edit the plan through the Offline Planner, Mobius will open the Offline Planner and allow the user to edit the given plan.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
