  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-SET-61345 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5484846"> Verification Test Cases </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 09:07:32 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 09:07:32 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Set Key:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VERTC</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3477765</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-SET-61345</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verification Test Cases</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description (Describe what the element set is trying to accomplish) :</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>RAASIC (Fill out the RAASIC table below):</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>The following RAASIC table is used to understand who needs to be involved in the lifecycle of the elements within this section.</p>
       <ul>
        <li>Enter all the Roles expected to participate in each of the categories.</li>
        <li>Approvers: It is expected that one or more personnel within the group listed&nbsp;is required to participate in the review process.</li>
        <li>Enter 'N/A' for fields deemed unnecessary.</li>
       </ul> <p><span style=3D"color:#e74c3c">&lt;Example of roles: Project Manager, Development Manager, Product Manager, Embedded, Safety, Mechanical, Electrical, Documentation, Training, GNC, ESO, PMO, PAT, Senior Leadership, Tech Lead, Support, Supply Chain, HR, Facilities, Director, VP, Customers, Stakeholders,&nbsp;etc.&gt;</span></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>
       <table border=3D"1" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" style=3D"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%">
        <thead>
         <tr>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Responsible</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) expected to&nbsp;work&nbsp;on the task.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Accountable</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) accountable for getting the task&nbsp;completed. They give the final approval and&nbsp;acts as a decision maker.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Approvers</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) accountable to&nbsp;ensure the task is completed&nbsp;to an acceptable level.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Support</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) helps the ones&nbsp;responsible and could actively work on the task.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Informed</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) requires&nbsp;information on the status, any decisions being made, and when the task is complete.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Consulted</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) offers&nbsp;advice or guidance&nbsp;but are not actively working on the task.</span></p></th>
         </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
         <tr>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
         </tr>
        </tbody>
       </table> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1202 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5322179"> MAP_SHAPES Waste Area </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 06:17:25 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 06:50:53 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1202</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3434827</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">MAP_SHAPES Waste Area</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>
         <div style=3D"--ak-renderer-base-font-size:14px; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h1:normal 600 1.71429em/1.16667 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h2:normal 600 1.42857em/1.2 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h3:normal 600 1.14286em/1.25 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h4:normal 600 1em/1.14286 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h5:normal 600 0.857143em/1.33333 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h6:normal 600 0.785714em/1.45455 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-normal-text:normal 400 1em/1.714 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif">
          <div>
           <p>I want a Waste Area shape available to map so that i can have the mower slow down over certain parts of the fairway</p>
          </div>
         </div></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map has been created and published</li>
        <li>A fairway on the map has been created</li>
        <li>The tester is using an administrator account in Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map has been created and published</li>
        <li>A fairway on the map has been created</li>
        <li>The tester is using an administrator account in Mobius</li>
        <li>Mobius Server is running</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client is running</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client is pointed to the IP address of the same build number (or newer) build of Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Simulation</li>
        <li>Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: With a map, that includes a fairway inside of a drivable area, has been published, navigate to the Maps section of Mobius.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Select a map to add the cart path shape to and click&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Edit selected map&lt;/em&gt;., The Maps section of Mobius will open, the user will be brought to the screen to edit the map.<br>2: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Click on the option to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Draw a free-form shape&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>   &lt;p&gt;Using the tool, create a rectangle that crosses a fairway. When the shape has been created, click the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Draw a free-form shape&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;tool again to deselect it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, The Shape Selection modal will pop up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;It will list who edited the shape most recently, the name of the shape, the type of shape, and the speed limit of the shape.&amp;nbsp;<br>3: From the drop down menu, select&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Waste Area.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Keep the toggle for&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Disengage Shapes&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;left off., The shape will change color to a dotted grey shape.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;The type will also state&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Waste Area&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;The speed limit defaults to 3.42 mph, but can be adjusted.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;There is a toggle that allows the user to select whether or not the shape will force the Offline Planner to create Action Points to lift the reels when the mower enters the Waste Area shape, and Action Points to lower the reels as the mower leaves the Waste Area shape.<br>4: Publish the map, and then navigate to the Offline Planner section of Mobius.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;With the fairway that now has a cart path across it, create a plan. None of the plan parameters matter, they can be left at their default values.&amp;nbsp;, Mobius will create a plan with that respects the speed set by the user for the Waste Area shape.&amp;nbsp;<br>5: Navigate back to the&amp;nbsp;Maps section of Mobius, select the newly created Waste Area shape, and change the toggle for Disengage Shapes to be on.&amp;nbsp;, Mobius will create a plan with Action Points that lift and lower the reels before and after the Waste Area shape, and will create a contiguous plan across the whole shape, and respect the speed set by the user when creating the shape.&amp;nbsp;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"CCFFCC" width=3D"80%">Low</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1201 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5322054"> MAP_SHAPES Cart Path </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 05:47:06 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 06:51:40 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1201</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3434767</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">MAP_SHAPES Cart Path</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>
         <div style=3D"--ak-renderer-base-font-size:14px; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h1:normal 600 1.71429em/1.16667 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h2:normal 600 1.42857em/1.2 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h3:normal 600 1.14286em/1.25 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h4:normal 600 1em/1.14286 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h5:normal 600 0.857143em/1.33333 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-heading-h6:normal 600 0.785714em/1.45455 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; --ak-renderer-editor-font-normal-text:normal 400 1em/1.714 &quot;Atlassian Sans&quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif">
          <div>
           <p>I want a cart path shape&nbsp;so that the mower disengage the reels when traveling across a cart path.</p>
          </div>
         </div></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map has been created and published</li>
        <li>A fairway on the map has been created</li>
        <li>The tester is using an administrator account in Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A map has been created and published</li>
        <li>A fairway on the map has been created</li>
        <li>The tester is using an administrator account in Mobius</li>
        <li>Mobius Server is running</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client is running</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop Client is pointed to the IP address of the same build number (or newer) build of Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Simulation</li>
        <li>Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Desktop Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: With a map, that includes a fairway inside of a drivable area, has been published, navigate to the Maps section of Mobius.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Select a map to add the cart path shape to and click&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Edit selected map&lt;/em&gt;., The Maps section of Mobius will open, the user will be brought to the screen to edit the map.<br>2: Click on the option to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Draw a free-form shape&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Using the tool, create a rectangle that crosses a fairway. When the shape has been created, click the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Draw a free-form shape&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;tool again to deselect it.&amp;nbsp;, The Shape Selection modal will pop up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;It will list who edited the shape most recently, the name of the shape, the type of shape, and the speed limit of the shape.&amp;nbsp;<br>3: From the drop down menu, select&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Cart Path&lt;/em&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;, The shape will change color to a hatched grey shape.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;The type will also state&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Cart Path&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;The speed limit defaults to 3.42 mph, but can be adjusted<br>4: Publish the map, and then navigate to the Offline Planner section of Mobius.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;With the fairway that now has a cart path across it, create a plan. None of the plan parameters matter, they can be left at their default values.&amp;nbsp;, Mobius will create a plan with Action Points that lift and lower the reels before and after the Cart Path, and will create a contiguous plan across the whole shape.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"CCFFCC" width=3D"80%">Low</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
