  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-977 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5164934"> Mobius Map Shape Objects </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">11/25/2025 09:23:34 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">11/25/2025 09:23:34 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-977</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3334792</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius Map Shape Objects</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius for Landscaping needs to have specific map shapes with specific behaviors and designs.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Map Editor</li>
        <li>Mobius Offline Planner</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Note any assumptions made prior to testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server is running with an empty map published.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Simulation</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server running either locally or on a test server</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: While Mobius Server and Desktop Client is running, navigate to the Maps section of Mobius. Create and place the following shapes using the pen tool.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;ul&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;Drivable Area&lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;/ul&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Create this shape in a very large square. At least 300 feet x 300 feet, When the Drivable Area shape has been created it will show as a white&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;color with a small black border.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"201" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/10813/image-cWM2ukem7Y.png" width=3D"199" /&gt;<br>2: &lt;p&gt;Inside the Drivable Area shape, create the following shapes&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;ul&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;An Outdoor Coverage Area that's 100x150&amp;nbsp;feet (a rectangle that fits inside the Drivable Area)&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;A Bunker off to one side&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;A Rough shape slightly larger than the Bunker shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;A Water Hazard off to another side&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;A Keep Out Area off to another side&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;A Disengage shape overlapping the Outdoor Coverage Area and the Drivable Area&lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;/ul&gt;, When all shapes have been placed, the following will be true for each shape&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;ul&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;Outdoor Coverage Area will be green and striped with alternating shades of green&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The Bunker shape will be tan with a dashed border inside the edge of the Bunker&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The Rough shape will show dark grey with black polka dots and a small black border&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The Water Hazard shape will be a blue color, blue border, and blue cross hatching&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The Keep Out Area will be a light red background with dark red stripes and a black border in the Maps section of Mobius. Once the map is published, the Keep Out Area will show as a white background with small black border and black stripes across the shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The Disengage Shape will show a similar pattern to the Outdoor Coverage Area shape, but will be light blue&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;/ul&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"200" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/10814/image-z0lfAN2BYt.png" width=3D"200" /&gt;<br>3: With this test drivable area and fairway with hazards created, publish the map and then navigate to the Offline Planner section of Mobius&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;While in the Offline Planner, create a new plan that with this fairway. None of the parameters for the plan matter, just as long as a plan is actually created., When the plan has been loaded, the following behaviors will be true for each shape&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;ul&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will show Action Points to lift and lower the reels when entering and exiting the Outdoor Coverage Area shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will always stay at least 1.1 meters from the Keep Out Area shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will get closer than 1.1 meters to the Bunker shape, but will never enter it&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will cross the Rough shape, but will not create action points in the Rough shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will not enter the Water Hazard Shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will create lift and lower action points when entering and exiting the Disengage shape&lt;/li&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;The plan will never leave the Drivable Area shape&lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;/ul&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"218" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/10815/image-vNfOYFQdfc.png" width=3D"200" /&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FFFF66" width=3D"80%">Medium</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1218 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5487133"> Verify Mower cannot operate within a mapped obstacle </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 06:51:16 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 07:53:06 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1218</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3478939</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mower cannot operate within a mapped obstacle</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mower shall not be able to operate when located within an obstacle on the map</li>
        <li>Related to&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/lib/requirements/reqView.php?&amp;showReqSpecTitle=3D1&amp;requirement_id=3D149450&amp;req_version_id=3D149451" target=3D"_blank">B-080202-01010100-1.0:Mobius shall not create a path through an obstacle</a></li>
        <li><a href=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/lib/requirements/reqView.php?&amp;showReqSpecTitle=3D1&amp;requirement_id=3D149592&amp;req_version_id=3D149593" target=3D"_blank">B-080301-01000860-1.2:Mobius shall prevent the vehicle from planning into obstacles</a></li>
        <li><a href=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/lib/requirements/reqView.php?&amp;showReqSpecTitle=3D1&amp;requirement_id=3D149594&amp;req_version_id=3D149595" target=3D"_blank">B-080301-09020020-1.0:Mobius shall prevent the vehicle from planning into obstacles 2.1</a></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mower is running an up to date and functional build of the VCU</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server &amp; Client</li>
        <li>Mower/Simulator checked into Mobius and powered on</li>
        <li>Mobius map created and published with an area coverage map shape</li>
        <li>Simulator/Mower located within the area coverage map shape</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
        <li>MOW SIL</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
        <li>MOW SIL</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: In the map editor, select the shape that contains the vehicle or create a shape around the vehicle, Shape Details will display with the ability to change the Type<br>2: Change shape type to obstacle, Map shape turns red<br>3: Publish map and return to the command screen, Map shape will be grey and vehicle will be in e-stop<br>4: Attempt to plan a waypoint&amp;nbsp;, No waypoint will be generated and vehicle will stay in e-stop<br>5: Attempt to clear estop through local confirmation, Vehicle will not leave the estop state</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
