  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1213 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5351967"> Verify WAT is available on the Command Screen </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/11/2026 09:09:14 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 05:59:39 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1213</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3452119</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify WAT is available on the Command Screen</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>​​​​​​Verify that the user can initiate a WAT on the Command Screen</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
        <li>SMU</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius&nbsp;is running</li>
        <li>Mower is checked into the Mobius and operating normally&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>User has moved the Mower checked into Mobius server to a clear area near an area coverage shape</li>
        <li>​​​​​​Mower has been assigned to User</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Real Mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A mower with an up to date SMU</li>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open mobius client and click on the mower in the command screen from the map, There will be a LiDAR section in the middle of the vehicle card. If the LiDAR test is required it will say "LiDAR Test Required" And will have a "Settings" button. If it is not required it will say "LiDAR Test" and say how many hours remaining until the test is required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"200" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/13082/image-jJtISVCi4n.png" width=3D"351" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"199" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/13081/image-X53JKuQlgt.png" width=3D"351" /&gt;<br>2: Click the "Settings" button, WAT will be opened</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1211 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5350970"> Verify Mobius Desktop Supports WAT Out of Sequence Zones </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/11/2026 05:43:01 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/11/2026 05:43:01 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1211</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3451497</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobius Desktop Supports WAT Out of Sequence Zones</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify Mobius Desktop UI supports the Out of Sequence Zone clearing fail state.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop</li>
        <li>SMU</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius&nbsp;is running</li>
        <li>Mower is checked into the Mobius and operating normally&nbsp;</li>
        <li>24 hours have passed since the most recent Walk-Around Test</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>User has moved the Mower checked into Mobius server to a clear area near an area coverage shape</li>
        <li>​​​​​​Mower has been assigned to User</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Real Mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A mower with an up to date SMU</li>
        <li>Mobius Desktop</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: With a mower assigned to you begin a WAT clearing the first zone, The first zone will be highlighted green<br>2: Move to another zone out of sequence, The zone will be highlighted red and "Missed a zone" will be displayed with&amp;nbsp;the timer no longer visible&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"304" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/12706/image-Kr59FwnaVZ.png" width=3D"451" /&gt;<br>3: Press the "Restart" button and clear the first zone again, then clear two separate zones out of sequence at the same time.&amp;nbsp;, The UI will reflect the two zones that were entered by highlighting them red and "Missed a zone" will be displayed with&amp;nbsp;the timer no longer visible</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1209 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5348439"> Verify Mobius Client UI supports WAT </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/10/2026 10:41:13 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/10/2026 11:09:11 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1209</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3450072</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobius Client UI supports WAT</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that Mobius Client supports the WAT UI.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
        <li>SMU</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius&nbsp;is running</li>
        <li>Mower is checked into the Mobius and operating normally&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>User has moved the Mower checked into Mobius server to a clear area near an area coverage shape</li>
        <li>​​​​​​Mower has been assigned to User</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Real Mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>A mower with an up to date SMU</li>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open Mobius client and open the settings screen selecting the vehicle intended for the WAT, LiDAR will be an option in the vehicle settings menu<br>2: Select the LiDAR option, The main LiDAR Sensor Check screen will be visible.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;<br>​​​​​​At the top of the screen will be "LIDAR SENSOR CHECK" under that there will be instructions on how to perform the WAT. "Move Sequentially from zone to zone. Stay within 1-5 meters from the mower." Under that there will be "Test required" and a semi-transparent version of the testing interface with a "Begin Sensor Test" button overlaid on top.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"259" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/12565/image-ehs5cKxpCQ.png" width=3D"451" /&gt;<br>3: Press the Begin Sensor check button, Testing interface will become more opaque and on the top left of the screen there will be a timer at 2:00 and on the top right there will be a "Restart" button which will be greyed out until the timer start.&amp;nbsp;<br>4: Step into one of the zones, The zone will be highlighted green and the timer will start. The "Restart" button will no longer be greyed out.&amp;nbsp;<br>5: Move sequentially from zone to zone, Each zone cleared will be highlighted green until all zones are cleared. "Sensor Check Successful" will be at the top of the screen with "Required in 24 hours"&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"336" src=3D"https://autonomoussolutions.jamacloud.com/attachment/12584/image-1xpbjMgBw9.png" width=3D"451" /&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
