  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1210 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5350569"> Verify Objective does not persist on server once cleared on mobius mobile </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/11/2026 05:00:54 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/12/2026 05:25:03 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1210</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3451445</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Objective does not persist on server once cleared on mobius mobile</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>To Verify that when mobius mobile&nbsp;is used to clear the assignment it does not persist on the server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
        <li>Mobius Server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong>​​​​​​​</p>
       <ul>
        <li>RW Mower or SIL checked into the server</li>
        <li>Map uploaded with plans created in the offline planner</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>SIL or RW mower moved to a driveable area with an area coverage shape and a plan created for that shape.</li>
        <li>Mower has been assigned to user.​​​​​</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Using the mobile app load up a plan and run the plan with the RW mower or SIL, Mower will execute the plan with no issues<br>2: Once the mower has completed a portion of the plan press the kebab menu on the bottom left of the command screen and press clear assignments, Mower will stop operation and objective will be cleared<br>3: Pull the Drawer up and press "change plan", select the "Select new plan"&amp;nbsp; and choose one of the available plans, History will be cleared and plan will load&amp;nbsp;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
