  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-SET-61358 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5484966"> Verification Test Cases </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 09:44:33 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 09:44:33 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Set Key:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VERTC</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3477797</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-SET-61358</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verification Test Cases</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description (Describe what the element set is trying to accomplish) :</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>RAASIC (Fill out the RAASIC table below):</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>The following RAASIC table is used to understand who needs to be involved in the lifecycle of the elements within this section.</p>
       <ul>
        <li>Enter all the Roles expected to participate in each of the categories.</li>
        <li>Approvers: It is expected that one or more personnel within the group listed&nbsp;is required to participate in the review process.</li>
        <li>Enter 'N/A' for fields deemed unnecessary.</li>
       </ul> <p><span style=3D"color:#e74c3c">&lt;Example of roles: Project Manager, Development Manager, Product Manager, Embedded, Safety, Mechanical, Electrical, Documentation, Training, GNC, ESO, PMO, PAT, Senior Leadership, Tech Lead, Support, Supply Chain, HR, Facilities, Director, VP, Customers, Stakeholders,&nbsp;etc.&gt;</span></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>
       <table border=3D"1" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" style=3D"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%">
        <thead>
         <tr>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Responsible</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) expected to&nbsp;work&nbsp;on the task.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Accountable</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) accountable for getting the task&nbsp;completed. They give the final approval and&nbsp;acts as a decision maker.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Approvers</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) accountable to&nbsp;ensure the task is completed&nbsp;to an acceptable level.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Support</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) helps the ones&nbsp;responsible and could actively work on the task.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Informed</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) requires&nbsp;information on the status, any decisions being made, and when the task is complete.</span></p></th>
          <th scope=3D"col" style=3D"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: 16.5%;"><p><span style=3D"font-size:12px"><u><strong>Consulted</strong></u></span></p> <p><span style=3D"font-size:8px">Role(s) offers&nbsp;advice or guidance&nbsp;but are not actively working on the task.</span></p></th>
         </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
         <tr>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
         </tr>
        </tbody>
       </table> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1203 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5331195"> User Assignment persists despite backgrounding the app </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/02/2026 09:23:34 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/03/2026 08:47:54 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1203</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3439330</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">User Assignment persists despite backgrounding the app</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>The User Assignment should persist if the app is backgrounded or the phone is closed.&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mower is signed into the server and checked in</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server is running</li>
        <li>Mobius Mobile is open and signed in</li>
        <li>​​​​​​Mower is signed into the server</li>
        <li>Mower is assigned to user</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Simulation</li>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open mobius mobile and assign a mower to your user account, Mower will assigned to your user account<br>2: Close the phone pressing the power button on the side and wait 5 minutes no user should reassign the mower during this time, then open the phone and the app, Mower will be reassigned to your account&amp;nbsp;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
