      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server&nbsp;</li>
        <li>Mobius App Installed on Mobile Device/Emulator (Currently only Android 4-15-2021)</li>
        <li>Multiple vehicles connected and checked into Mobius</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong>​​​​​​</p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open Mobile App, The application opens<br>2: Navigate to the User Assignment page, All users logged into the server and all mowers checked into the server will be visible</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
