  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1220 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5487387"> Verify Mobius stops mower when clear assignment is clicked in mobile </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 08:50:49 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 08:50:49 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1220</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3478996</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobius stops mower when clear assignment is clicked in mobile</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify Mobius shall stop the vehicle/simulator when clear assignment is clicked when vehicle/simulator is in motion</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mower is running the most up to date and functional VCU build</li>
        <li>Mobius server and mobile app</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius mobile&nbsp;and server</li>
        <li>Vehicle/simulator checked into Mobius</li>
        <li>Map published with drivable area and area coverage shape with a plan created in offline planner</li>
        <li>Vehicle/simulator located within drivable area</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
        <li>Mow SIL</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
        <li>Mow SIL</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Load plan using the mobile app for the vehicle, Plan will generate<br>2: Start execution of the plan&amp;nbsp;, Mower will begin to execute the plan<br>3: Press the vertical ellipsis on the bottom left of the mobile app and then press 'clear assignments", Mower will begin to slow down and stop execution and plan will be cleared</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1223 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5488478"> Verify Mobile local confirmation implementation </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 10:43:42 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 10:43:42 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1223</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3480003</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobile local confirmation implementation</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>We want to verify that local confirmation is fully implemented on the mobile app</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest stable mobile app build&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mower is connected to the server</li>
        <li>Mower is placed near a fairway</li>
        <li>Mower is assigned to tester</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>RW-Mower</li>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open the mobile app&amp;nbsp;, There should be a "Select Plan button on the bottom with a draw and a vertical ellipses button and a follow mower button&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"400" src=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/third_party/asiUserFiles/files/shared%20image.jpg" width=3D"180" /&gt;<br>2: Press "Select Plan"&amp;nbsp;, The Drawer shall open sliding up from the bottom of the screen with plans listed available to run<br>3: Select a plan and press use plan after the plan has been validated, The planning drawer will lower and the "Select Plan" button will be replaces with "Hold to Start" which is grey and below that it will say "Please toggle the Auto Manual switch" along with an "Important" "Safety Check Required- Clear the area, inspect under the mower for obstructions, and confirm readiness." message&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"400" src=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/third_party/asiUserFiles/files/shared%20image%20(2).jpg" width=3D"180" /&gt;<br>4: Toggle the Auto Manual switch on the mower after inspecting for obstacles and obstructions, The "Hold to Start" button will disappear until the mower finishes loading. Then the "Hold to Start" button will turn green with the bar below indicating the time remaining before another local confirmation will be required, there will be a message that shows the number of seconds "remaining to start"&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"400" src=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/third_party/asiUserFiles/files/shared%20image%20(3).jpg" width=3D"180" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;<br>5: Press the "Hold to Start" button to start the mower before the timer is up, The mower will begin to power on, clear estop, and start the plan. There will be an indicator on the screen to show the progress the mower has made&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=3D"text-align:center"&gt;&lt;img alt=3D"" height=3D"110" src=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/third_party/asiUserFiles/files/shared%20image%20(5).jpg" width=3D"180" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;<br>6: The mower will begin to execute the plan if all steps pass. Pause the mower if it does, The green hold to start will appear without the countdown but with a Warning Message<br>7: Hold the "Hold to Start" button to start the mower running again, The mower will start back up<br>8: Trigger a hazard zone violation, The mower should stop and the screen should return to Local Confirmation required screen seen in step 3 and the mower will not be able to begin until the auto manual button is toggled on the physical mower</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
