  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1224 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5488496"> Verify Mobius mobile requires user account to access it </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 11:04:21 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/24/2026 11:09:46 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1224</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3480006</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobius mobile requires user account to access it</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that a user cannot access the mobile application without first signing in with a valid user account</li>
        <li>User does not have to log in every time, as long as Mobius Server has login session management</li>
        <li>Related to:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/lib/requirements/reqView.php?&amp;showReqSpecTitle=3D1&amp;requirement_id=3D191197&amp;req_version_id=3D191198" target=3D"_blank">SPEC-AUG-MVP-090402-00000220:MOBIUS Mobile Application MUST login MOBIUS Server by user account when use</a></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest stable build of mobius mobile is installed and is valid for the version of mobius server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Server and Client running</li>
        <li>User account has been created and logged to mobius with the same user account</li>
        <li>Related to:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/lib/requirements/reqView.php?&amp;showReqSpecTitle=3D1&amp;requirement_id=3D191197&amp;req_version_id=3D191198" target=3D"_blank">SPEC-AUG-MVP-090402-00000220:MOBIUS Mobile Application MUST login MOBIUS Server by user account when use.</a></li>
        <li><a href=3D"https://testlink.asirobots.com/lib/requirements/reqView.php?&amp;showReqSpecTitle=3D1&amp;requirement_id=3D207118&amp;req_version_id=3D207119" target=3D"_blank">B-090402-00000220-1.0:Mobius Mobile application shall support user login</a></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Mobile</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open Mobile application and enter the server IP the user account was created for then press confirm, Login Screen will open<br>2: Attempt to access application without attempting to enter any login credentials, Application remains at login page. No other functions available<br>3: Attempt to login using improper credentials&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;1. Improper ID&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;2. Improper Password&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;3. Improper Password and ID, The mobile app will respond with "Authentication failed: verify the username and password."<br>4: Attempt to login using proper credentials, User will be able to successfully log into application</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1225 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5498103"> Verify Mobile App allows follow vehicle and continuous follow while zooming </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/27/2026 12:16:00 AM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/27/2026 12:16:01 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1225</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3484755</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Mobile App allows follow vehicle and continuous follow while zooming</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that the Mobile&nbsp;app follow function works correctly in different scenarios</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile app is compatible with the server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Desktop and server are running</li>
        <li>Simulator or Physical mower are checked in and assigned to the mobile app user's account</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
        <li>SIL&nbsp;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobile App</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Open the mobile app with the mower assigned to the login used on the mobile app, By default when the mower is assigned to the user the "follow" button to the left of the play/pause button will be blue indicating that follow mode is activated<br>2: Take the vehicle away from mobile user and start a second simulator then assign both vehicles at the same time to the mobile user, Neither mower should have follow mode activated<br>3: Select one of the vehicles in the mobile app by tapping the mower icon on the map, Vehicle will automatically be followed after selection<br>4: Assign a plan or path for the vehicle selected. On mobile app there should be a button on bottom right that looks similar to the desktop app follow button. Click button to turn on or off multiple times, Follow vehicle button is clickable and the color changes when clicked on or off<br>5: Execute path for vehicle and turn on follow vehicle button, Vehicle is followed<br>6: While following vehicle, zoom in and out, Follow function should stay on.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;It may not stay following 100% of the time but that is not a fail. If erratic enough it is possible to break)<br>7: While following vehicle, pan or move around, Follow function will turn off and symbol will turn grey to indicate follow is turned off</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTC-1226 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5594989"> Verify Too Far from start of path is fixed </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">03/05/2026 05:35:53 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/05/2026 06:18:32 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTC-1226</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3494965</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Too Far from start of path is fixed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Formal Review</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>When stopping the mower on a cleanup lap and resuming too far from start of path error should not occur.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
        <li>Mobius Server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest stable build of mobius is running on the server and client</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Plan has been created for a area coverage shape in a driveable area</li>
        <li>Mower is checked into the server</li>
        <li>Load plan for area coverage shape</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Client</li>
        <li>Mobius Server</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>SIL, HIL, MowRW</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Begin execution of the plan with the mower running until the cleanup lap, Mower will execute the plan<br>2: Pause the mower while running the cleanup lap, Mower will come to a complete stop<br>3: Move the mower away from the cleanup lap and toggle the auto manual, A path will be generated to connect to the cleanup lap with no errors<br>4: Repeat steps 2 and 3, three more times as the mower moves through the cleanup lap, The behavior should be unchanged<br>5: Press play and allow the mower to complete the plan, There will be no errors while it finishes the cleanup lap and plan</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">No</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Manual</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
