  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-1 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101204"> Verify SMU initializes using the Customized DuplicaTTor framework </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:10:57 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:15:25 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-1</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302100</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify SMU initializes using the Customized DuplicaTTor framework</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that the SMU initializes correctly when the Vehicle Autonomous Kit (VAK) is powered on, and that the Customized DuplicaTTor framework engages to support SMU self-tests at startup.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Covers SMU initialization behavior in both Software-in-the-Loop (SIL) and Hardware-in-the-Loop (HIL) environments. Confirms that the SMU begins its self-test sequence to ensure internal fault detection within the specified response time (&lt; 50 ms).</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Latest testable version of SMU software is loaded and verified.</p></li>
        <li><p>SMU is correctly installed in the VAK with all required connections.</p></li>
        <li><p>SIL/HIL test environments are available and configured for automated execution.</p></li>
        <li><p>Diagnostic channels and logging are enabled for monitoring SMU status and fault reporting.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>“Current” version of SMU software is loaded onto the SMU.</p></li>
        <li><p>SIL or HIL test environment is ready to power on.</p></li>
        <li><p>Customized DuplicaTTor logging/diagnostic monitoring is active.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>SIL with SIM-SMU</li>
        <li>HIL with SMU</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL simulator hardware/software platform</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL test rig with SMU and VAK hardware</p></li>
        <li><p>Logging/diagnostic monitoring tools (e.g., CAN logger, DuplicaTTor console output)</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p><strong>(TBD)</strong> Expected console/log initialization message</p></li>
        <li><p><strong>(TBD)</strong> Diagnostic messages for simulated internal fault conditions</p></li>
        <li><p><strong>(TBD)</strong> Timing data from power-on to SMU initialization complete</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Ensure SIL or HIL environment is powered and ready., SMU will be powered on.<br>2: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Apply VAK power to initialize the SMU.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Observe initialization sequence in DuplicaTTor logs.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>4: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Confirm that console/log output shows successful framework initialization.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Verify that no fault diagnostics appear during startup.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
