  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-8 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101259"> Verify fail-safe if SMU does not command stop at slope ≥ 25° </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:27:27 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:27:27 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-8</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302150</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify fail-safe if SMU does not command stop at slope ≥ 25°</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that if the mower enters a slope ≥ 25° and the SMU fails to issue a stop command, the system transitions to a fail-safe state.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Covers the negative path, ensuring SMU cannot allow mower to continue autonomous operation beyond safe slope limits.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Fault injection or override available to simulate SMU failure to issue stop.</p></li>
        <li><p>Diagnostic telemetry supports detection of missing stop command (TBD).</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mower in autonomous mode with slope path configured (TBD) with Programmatic overrides or Telemetry Service commands.</p></li>
        <li><p>Fault injection prepared (SMU stop command disabled).</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL with simulated slope and suppressed stop command</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL with overridden SMU behavior</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL simulator with fault injection</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL rig with slope course and override capability</p></li>
        <li><p>Diagnostic/logging tools</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>(Subject to Change) Path_Steep_Slope Only_4mph, 6mph, 8mph</p></li>
        <li><p>Expected failure diagnostics (TBD)</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Initialize SIL/HIL mower in autonomous mode.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>2: Command SIL/HIL to drive a path while adjusting a telemetry override that matches a slope path heading in to (≥ 25°).<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Suppress/disable SMU stop command.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>4: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Verify Telemetry SIL/HIL mower still in motion&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;(TBD) Verify SIL/HIL mower transitions to fail-safe state.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>6: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;(TBD)&amp;nbsp;Verify diagnostic/log messages indicate stop failure.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FF0000" width=3D"80%">Critical / Safety</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-9 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101261"> Verify stop occurs within required &lt;response time&gt; (TBD) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:28:54 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:28:54 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-9</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302152</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify stop occurs within required &lt;response time&gt; (TBD)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that the SMU issues a stop command within the required (TBD) seconds after detecting slope ≥ 25°.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Confirms compliance with time-response requirements for slope detection and safety stop behavior.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Latest “testable” SMU software version loaded.</p></li>
        <li><p>IMU telemetry services for slope detection are available (or overridden for automation).</p></li>
        <li><p>Vehicle is operating in autonomous mode.</p></li>
        <li><p>IMU telemetry provides slope data with (TBD) accuracy.</p></li>
        <li><p>Timing measurement tools are available in SIL/HIL environments.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mower in autonomous mode.</p></li>
        <li><p>Timing capture tools active.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL with slope simulation and timing logs</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL with slope course and high-resolution timing capture</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Simulator with timing/logging hooks</p></li>
        <li><p>Physical mower + slope test area with timing sensors/logging</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Path_Steep_4mph, 6mph, 8mph</p></li>
        <li><p>Timestamps for slope detection and stop command</p></li>
        <li><p>Diagnostic stop messages</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Initialize SIL/HIL mower in autonomous mode.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>2: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Command SIL/HIL to Drive onto slope path ≥ 25°.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Capture timestamp at slope detection.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>4: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Capture timestamp at SMU stop command.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Calculate elapsed time.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>6: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Verify elapsed time ≤ (TBD) seconds.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>7: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Confirm diagnostic/logs reflect slope detection and stop event.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-10 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101266"> Verify mower stops at exactly 25° slope (threshold boundary) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:34:08 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 05:34:08 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-10</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302155</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify mower stops at exactly 25° slope (threshold boundary)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify that when the mower encounters a slope of exactly 25°, the SMU issues a stop command and the mower comes to a complete stop.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Covers slope detection at the exact threshold value to confirm there is no ambiguity in stop behavior. Ensures compliance with the requirement that ≥25° triggers safety stop.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Latest testable version of SMU software is loaded.</p></li>
        <li><p>IMU telemetry services report slope angles with (TBD) accuracy.</p></li>
        <li><p>Vehicle is operating in autonomous mode.</p></li>
        <li><p>Map/path setup allows mower to reach a stable slope of exactly 25°.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mower powered on in autonomous mode.</p></li>
        <li><p>Slope path configured to reach exactly 25°.</p></li>
        <li><p>Diagnostic/logging capture tools enabled.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL with slope injection set to 25°</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL with controlled slope test course</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL simulator with IMU injection</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL mower + slope track at 25°</p></li>
        <li><p>CAN/logger tools or Mobius console</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Path_Steep_25deg (new variant or adjusted slope path)</p></li>
        <li><p>Expected stop diagnostics for slope ≥25°</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Initialize mower in autonomous mode.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>2: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Drive mower onto slope path configured at exactly 25°.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Observe IMU telemetry slope =3D 25°.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>4: Verify SMU issues stop command within (TBD) seconds.<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Verify mower halts before slope increases.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>6: Confirm diagnostic/log messages report slope 25° and stop.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
