       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Detail the required system state or setup before testing begins.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Include hardware/software configurations, test benches, or simulation tools.</span>&gt;</li>
