  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-15 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101284"> Verify Up/Down Prioritization Part 1 Drop </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 06:27:47 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 06:27:47 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-15</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302170</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Up/Down Prioritization Part 1 Drop</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify&nbsp;Vehicle starts driving with reels up, then down, then lifts into transport mode, then drops all the way down.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Only testing Up/Down Priority Actions and States while driving.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>None</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>“Current” version of VCU&nbsp;software configured with Reels.</p></li>
        <li><p>“Current” versions of Mobius&nbsp;software.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mobius includes the Offline Planner Module.</p></li>
        <li><p>Valid Small Area&nbsp;Map</p></li>
        <li><p>UpDnConflict Plan&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>SIL and or HIL</li>
        <li>Mobius Planner</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL simulator hardware/software platform</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL test rig with SMU and VAK hardware</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Map: Preston on Test Fairway - Linked below</p></li>
        <li><p>Plan: UpDnConflict_Plan.json - Linked below</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Set Settings/[Mower]/VCU configuration&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>2: Set the reels.actionBuffer.durationDropMsec to 950<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Set the reels.actionBuffer.durationLiftMsec to 1150&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;All The DKS values should change successfully&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>4: Load the UpDnconflict plan for a test fairway map<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Execute the plan&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Then the mower will start driving with the reels up,&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>   &lt;p&gt;Then motion the reels down,&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>   &lt;p&gt;Then completely lift the reels,&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>   &lt;p&gt;Then immediately drop the reels&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FF0000" width=3D"80%">Critical / Safety</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-16 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101285"> Verify Up/Down Prioritization Part 2 Lift-Transport-Mode </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 06:29:26 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 06:29:26 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-16</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302171</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify Up/Down Prioritization Part 2 Lift-Transport-Mode</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Verify&nbsp;Vehicle starts driving with reels up,&nbsp;then down, then lifts into transport mode.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Only testing Up/Down Priority Actions and States while driving.</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>None</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>“Current” version of VCU&nbsp;software configured with Reels.</p></li>
        <li><p>“Current” versions of Mobius&nbsp;software.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mobius includes the Offline Planner Module.</p></li>
        <li><p>Valid Small Area&nbsp;Map</p></li>
        <li><p>UpDnConflict Plan&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>SIL and or HIL</li>
        <li>Mobius Planner</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>SIL simulator hardware/software platform</p></li>
        <li><p>HIL test rig with SMU and VAK hardware</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Map: Preston on Test Fairway - Linked below</p></li>
        <li><p>Plan: UpDnConflict_Plan.json - Linked below</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Set Settings/[Mower]/VCU configuration<br>2: Set the reels.actionBuffer.durationDropMsec to 1150<br>3: Set the reels.actionBuffer.durationLiftMsec to 950, All the DKS values should change successfully<br>4: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Load the UpDnconflict plan for the test fairway in preston&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>5: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Execute the plan&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Then the mower will start driving with the reels up,&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>   &lt;p&gt;Then motions the reels down,&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>   &lt;p&gt;Then lifts into transport mode.&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
