  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-19 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5101289"> Verify no patch swaths in a newly created plan </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/16/2025 06:34:27 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 02:54:44 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-19</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3302174</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Verify no patch swaths in a newly created plan</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verify no patch swaths in a newly created plan</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Given a fairway to create a plan for</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; When Patching is toggled off in connect swaths</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; And the plan has completed</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Then there shall be no patch swaths in the plan</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Specify the boundaries of the test (e.g., subsystem, complete system).</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Note any assumptions made prior to testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Detail the required system state or setup before testing begins.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Include hardware/software configurations, test benches, or simulation tools.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">List all tools, instruments, and simulators used during testing.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>&lt;<span style=3D"color:#3498db">Provide input data or test conditions required for execution.</span>&gt;</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Go to offline planning&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>2: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Go through the steps to create a new plan for a fairway&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>3: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Toggling Patching to off in the Connect Swaths section&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>4: &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;Then finish the plan&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;, &lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>   &lt;td&gt;<br>   &lt;p&gt;There should be no patch swaths in the plan.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br>   &lt;/td&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Unassigned</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1964</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
