  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-TXT-124 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5104213"> Added Action Points get added for Lifting and Lowering Reels </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">10/20/2025 04:08:01 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">10/20/2025 04:08:01 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-TXT-124</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3304035</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Added Action Points get added for Lifting and Lowering Reels</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Validate that user added action points for lifting and lower reels, are added to path builder paths, then lift and lower the reels.&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assertion:&nbsp;</strong>Loading a Path with Action Points Loads, Running the path Action Points Lift and Lower the Reels.&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Resources:</strong><br> &nbsp; - Path Plan: AG-1801 Deck Action Points (Artifact ID: PLAN-AG-1801 v3)<br> &nbsp; - Map: GolfCourse-East-2024Q3 (Artifact ID: MAP-GC-EAST v7)</p> <p>&nbsp; - ReelActionPoints: required</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.&nbsp;RunSafeStartupSequence (Setup)</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.&nbsp;Landscaping/Paths/AG-1801 Deck Action Points.mobius.path.json (File)</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Automation Framework:</strong> Test-Platform</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Execution Environment</strong>: CI Pipeline - "Nightly Regression Runs"</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Pass/Fail Criteria (one-liner):</strong>&nbsp;Test needs to pass nightly run</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Verification Method:</strong> Test -- Options: "Test,” “Analysis,” or “Demonstration"</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Results:</strong>&nbsp;Results captured via CI logs</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Object Type:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">Information</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">AG_1801</td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-37 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5128401"> Mobius: Mower Dimension Service Verify mower Vehicle Width Blade To Blade Meters matches the VCU Configuration settings. </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">11/03/2025 09:13:33 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 10:44:06 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-37</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3315965</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Mower Dimension Service Verify mower Vehicle Width Blade To Blade Meters matches the VCU Configuration settings.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verifies that the mower Vehicle Width Blade To Blade Meters&nbsp; matches the VCU Configuration settings.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Planner to VCU Mower Settings</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Assumes the latest build of the AreaCoverageLibraries to be v22.1.0</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobius app installed and running with "AreaCoverageLibraries v22.1.0" integrated</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; A Mower is loaded on the map.</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Known Right and Left Blade dimensions expected 2.54</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Map Loaded</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest SIL/VCU Build: sbr_mower_90e63a890a_1092</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Current expected blade to blade width: 2.54</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Get mower blade to blade dimensions, Blade to Blade dimensions retrieved&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;**We expect the VCU value from&amp;nbsp; mowVehicleWidthBladeToBladeMeters to be 2.54<br>2: Create Offline Plan, &lt;p&gt;Offline Plan created&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;table&gt;<br> &lt;tbody&gt;<br>  &lt;tr&gt;<br>  &lt;/tr&gt;<br> &lt;/tbody&gt;<br>&lt;/table&gt;<br>3: Export new offline plan, Offline plan exported<br>4: Load exported plan and verify blade to blade dimensions, Exported plan loads and verify dimensions match</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
