  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-38 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5140638"> VCU: Verify Hazard and Standoff faults get triggered and estopped with machine speed variability </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">11/07/2025 09:32:08 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/12/2026 07:29:30 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-38</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3322886</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Verify Hazard and Standoff faults get triggered and estopped with machine speed variability</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verifies that the mowers Hazard and Standoff faults get triggered with machine speed variability</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius Telemetry and&nbsp;VCU notifications and faults</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Assumes the latest build of the AreaCoverageLibraries to be v22.1.0</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobius app installed and running with "AreaCoverageLibraries v22.1.0" integrated</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; A Mower is loaded on the map.</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Known and expected Faults:&nbsp;0xC708 -&nbsp;ZHazard,&nbsp;0xC70D -&nbsp;ZStandoff &amp;&nbsp;Estopped&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Map Loaded -&nbsp;SmallMowingMap</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest SIL/VCU Build: sbr_mower_90e63a890a_1092</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Current expected Faults:&nbsp;0xC708 -&nbsp;ZHazard,&nbsp;0xC70D -&nbsp;ZStandoff &amp;&nbsp;Estopped&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Update speed(s) on map and publish&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Assign way point to drive with a velocity&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Play the plan&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Wait till velocity is reached<br>2: Trigger ZHazard with: sim.VaiSim.ZHazard.PosX, 1, Hazard code was posted&amp;nbsp;0xC708&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Velocity went to 0&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Vehicle is estopped&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;<br>3: Reset the ZHazard Trigger&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Verify code is no longer present&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Toggle Auto&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Toggle Manual&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Clear Local Confir&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Power Engine On&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Continue running&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Wait till velocity is reached, Verify code is no longer present<br>4: Trigger zStandoff with: sim.VaiSim.ZStandoff.PosX, 1, Standoff code was posted&amp;nbsp;0xC70D&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Velocity went to 0<br>5: Set the new speed&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;ClearAssignment&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;RepeatSteps 1 and 2 at the new speed, Hazard code was posted&amp;nbsp;0xC708&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Velocity went to 0&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Vehicle is estopped&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Standoff code was posted 0xC70D&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Velocity went to 0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Failed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-39 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5149614"> VCU: Truth Table - Manual Mode - No Beacons or Audio </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">11/13/2025 01:53:35 AM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/27/2026 10:45:19 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-39</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3326992</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Truth Table - Manual Mode - No Beacons or Audio</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verifies that the mower in Manual mode prints&nbsp;no Beacon or Audio Telemetry to the console</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius to power the&nbsp;Mower</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobius app installed and running with&nbsp;the latest build of the VCU SIL</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; A Mower is loaded on the map.</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Known&nbsp;Audio and Beacon States</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Map to Loaded</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest SIL/VCU Build</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Expected Audio and Beacon States</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Mower is powered on and in Manual Mode<br>2: Verify Beacon States, Expect No Beacons will be active</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
