     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-44 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5150222"> VCU: Truth Table - Autonomous Mode | Crank Motion Wrn | TealSolid-AmberSlow-AudioA </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
