      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verifies that the mower in Initial Autonomous mode, with engine started just before running a mission, expect the Teal Beacon to be Solid&nbsp;&amp; Amber Beacon to be Flashing Slowly&nbsp;and Audio A states.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Mobius to power the&nbsp;Mower and set Initial Autonomous mode</li>
        <li>Monitor Start up to Running a mission for state</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobius app installed and running with&nbsp;the latest build of the VCU SIL</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; A Mower is loaded on the map.</p></li>
        <li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Known&nbsp;Audio and Beacon States</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></li>
       </ul> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Map to Loaded</li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li>Latest SIL/VCU Build</li>
