  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-51 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5171041"> VCU: Verify Velocity at Distance Condition Fault 0x0121 </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/04/2025 06:37:52 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/27/2026 01:03:50 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-51</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3338114</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Verify Velocity at Distance Condition Fault 0x0121</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verify that the VCU correctly triggers Velocity-at-Distance Condition Fault 0x0121 when velocity-at-distance messages from the VAI stop arriving, and that the mower safely stops as a result.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.</p></li>
        <li><p>The mower is actively running a plan.</p></li>
        <li><p>The VAI stops sending velocity-at-distance messages, and the VCU does not receive either the stopped or stopping velocity-at-distance message sources within 3 seconds.</p></li>
        <li><p>The test covers detection, fault reporting, and vehicle stop behavior after the VCU identifies the loss of VAI message updates.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>The current test build of the VCU (SIL or HIL) and Mobius Server/Hubs is installed, functional, and consistent with the integration branch being validated.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mobius and the VCU are configured to produce and log Fault 0x0121 as expected.</p></li>
        <li><p>The test environment supports mocking or simulating VAI message disruption (or rebooting the VAI process) to induce loss of velocity-at-distance messages.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mobius application is installed and running with the current AreaCoverageLibraries integrated.</p></li>
        <li><p>A mower asset is loaded on the map and capable of running a plan.</p></li>
        <li><p>Expected and allowable faults during the test include: Velocity-at-Distance Condition Fault 0x0121.</p></li>
        <li><p>The test environment provides the ability to mock, simulate, or interrupt VAI message flow or reboot the VAI module.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mobius Server and Mobius Hubs are connected and operational in either SIL, HIL, or SIM-based test mode.</p></li>
        <li><p>Network connectivity between Mobius, VAI, and the VCU is stable prior to inducing the fault condition.</p></li>
        <li><p>Logging is enabled and configured to capture VCU telemetry, plan execution states, velocity-at-distance messages, and triggered fault codes.</p></li>
        <li><p>The test area contains a valid coverage map with a defined plan that the mower can run continuously until the induced message loss occurs.</p></li>
        <li><p>No additional environmental overrides (DKS, debug flags, or VCU special modes) are active unless explicitly required.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Simulated mower running the current VCU software build under test.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mobius Hub workstation or simulator machine capable of sending command/control and capturing telemetry.</p></li>
        <li><p>VAI module or simulated VAI message generator that allows controlled disruption of velocity-at-distance messages.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>A valid plan file uploaded to Mobius (coverage pattern, endpoint, and path consistent with mower capability).</p></li>
        <li><p>Expected fault reference: Velocity-at-Distance Condition Fault 0x0121.</p></li>
        <li><p>Timing threshold for message timeout: 3 seconds for both stopped and stopping velocity-at-distance messages.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mower configuration:</p></li>
        <li><p>Vehicle ID and simulator name (if applicable)</p></li>
        <li><p>Default operational parameters (speed, thresholds, safety settings)</p></li>
        <li><p>Any reference telemetry or baseline logs showing normal VAI message frequency prior to disruption.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Mower is powered on&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set to Autonomous Mode&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Started on a Plan<br>2: For SIL Set the Velocity at Distance Condition Fault 0x0121 with (.ActivateSimulatedErrorCodes(0x0121)&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;For HIL Reboot the VAI, Velocity at Distance Fault 0x0121 Condition is triggered&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Vehicle is stopped (Velocity comes to 0)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FF0000" width=3D"80%">Critical / Safety</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-52 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5171044"> VCU: Vehicle MUST NOT allow autonomous operation when the park brake dks is set to not be enabled </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/04/2025 06:46:53 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/09/2026 03:00:36 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-52</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3338117</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Vehicle MUST NOT allow autonomous operation when the park brake dks is set to not be enabled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verify that the VCU correctly triggers Velocity-at-Distance Condition Fault 0x0121 when velocity-at-distance messages from the VAI stop arriving, and that the mower safely stops as a result.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Test covers the VCU’s enforcement of the Park Brake DKS requirement during autonomous operation.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mobius issues an autonomous start request and the VCU must reject or halt operation when Park Brake is not enabled.</p></li>
        <li><p>Applies to SIL, HIL, or simulator-based testing.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Current builds of Mobius and the VCU support reading and enforcing Park Brake DKS.</p></li>
        <li><p>Automation has the ability to set or override DKS parameters.</p></li>
        <li><p>The simulator can enter a ready state but must not transition into autonomous movement when Park Brake is disabled.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mobius is running with a vehicle loaded and capable of running autonomous plans.</p></li>
        <li><p>Park Brake DKS is set to Not Enabled prior to issuing an autonomous start command.</p></li>
        <li><p>The vehicle is powered on and in a state where it would normally be allowed to enter autonomous mode.</p></li>
        <li><p>The following needs to be set with DKS for the correct state:&nbsp;</p>
         <ul>
          <li><p>.SetDksValue("JohnDeereMower.parkbrake.debug", 1)</p></li>
          <li><p>.SetDksValue("johnDeereRelay.overrideNegDisable.parkBrakeEnable", 0)</p></li>
          <li><p>.SetDksValue("johnDeereRelay.overrideNegDisable.parkBrake", 1),</p></li>
         </ul></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Connected Mobius Server and Hubs (SIL/HIL/SIM environment acceptable).</p></li>
        <li><p>Standard logging enabled to capture state transitions, DKS evaluation, and VCU mode responses.</p>
         <ul>
          <li><p>No other DKS overrides applied unless required by the test.</p></li>
         </ul></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>One mower or simulator running the current VCU build.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Valid plan or autonomous start request.</p></li>
        <li><p>Park Brake DKS expected values:</p></li>
        <li><p>Expected VCU Fault Condition 0x9B08</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Mower is powered on&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set to Autonomous Mode&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set the Parking Brake State<br>2: Command the vehicle to drive, Vehicle should be e-stopped and SHALL NOT come out of estop while parking brake is manually disengaged.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FF0000" width=3D"80%">Critical / Safety</td>
     </tr>
