  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-53 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5171048"> VCU: Verify the following faults stop the vehicle Occlusion-0xC709 VAICommsTimeout-0xC70C </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/04/2025 06:53:41 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/12/2026 07:23:58 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-53</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3338119</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Verify the following faults stop the vehicle Occlusion-0xC709 VAICommsTimeout-0xC70C</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Objective:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Verify the following faults stop the vehicle for&nbsp;Occlusion-0xC709 VAICommsTimeout-0xC70C</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Scope:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Test covers VCU behavior when safety-critical fault conditions occur during autonomous operation.</p></li>
        <li><p>Mobius commands the vehicle into autonomous mode, and the automation triggers each fault independently.</p></li>
        <li><p>The VCU must transition out of autonomous operation and execute a controlled stop for each of the listed faults.</p></li>
        <li><p>Applies to SIL, HIL, or SIM-based test configurations.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Current Mobius and VCU builds support generating and reporting these three fault codes.</p></li>
        <li><p>Automation has the ability to mock or induce each fault condition independently.</p></li>
        <li><p>The simulator or mower can enter autonomous mode under normal conditions.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p><strong style=3D"font-style:normal">Preconditions:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Mobius is running with a SIM Vehicle asset loaded and capable of entering autonomous operation.</p></li>
        <li><p>A valid autonomous plan is available for execution.</p></li>
        <li><p>Vehicle is powered on and in a state eligible to begin autonomous movement.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Environment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Connected Mobius Server and Hubs (SIL/HIL/SIM environment acceptable).</p></li>
        <li><p>Standard logging enabled to capture fault generation, state transitions, and stop behavior.</p></li>
        <li><p>No additional DKS overrides applied unless required by the test scenario.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Equipment:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>One mower or simulator running the current VCU software build.</p></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Test Data:</strong></p>
       <ul>
        <li><p>Plan</p></li>
        <li><p>Expected VCU stop behavior for each fault</p></li>
        <li><p>Fault codes to be validated:</p>
         <ul>
          <li><p>0xC709 – Occlusion Zone Violated</p></li>
          <li><p>0xC70C – VAI Comms Timeout</p></li>
         </ul></li>
       </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Mower is powered on&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set to Autonomous Mode&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Started on a Plan<br>2: Set the Fault: 0xc709 - Occlusion Zone Violated with&amp;nbsp;"sim.VaiSim.ZOcclusion.PosX", 1, Fault&amp;nbsp;0xC709 is in telemetry and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Vehicle velocity comes to 0<br>3: Recover Vehicle to running the plan<br>4: Set the Fault: 0xC70C - VAI Comms Timeout with&amp;nbsp;ActivateSimulatedErrorCodes(0xC70C), Fault&amp;nbsp;0xC70C is in telemetry and&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Vehicle velocity comes to 0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Failed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FF0000" width=3D"80%">Critical / Safety</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-54 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213334"> Mobius: Client can set Maximum Speed of Autonomous Vehicle </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:54 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/12/2026 07:24:56 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-54</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371329</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Client can set Maximum Speed of Autonomous Vehicle</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verifies that when the mowers speed is set in Mobius that the vehicle drives at the set speed<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Changing vehicle speed.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL/HIL</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>Preconditions:<br> • Mobius app installed and running with latest version of "AreaCoverageLibraries" integrated<br> • Map is published in mobius.<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> <br> Environment:<br> • Map Loaded - SmallMowingMap.<br> • Enough area to run at speed.<br> <br> Equipment:<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build.<br> <br> Test Data:<br> • Map.<br> • Expected Speed for mower to reach 5 mph and not go over</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Mobiushub set speed with DKS to 5mph, DKS set to 5mph<br>2: Mobiushub Assign Plan to Mower, Plan is assigned<br>3: Mobiushub Begin running the plan, Mower starts running the plan and increases speed<br>4: Check recorded telemetry and verify, Verify telemetry and that the mower reached 5mph</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Failed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-887</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-55 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213335"> Mobius: Planner: Planner will plan waypoints around a map shape obstacle and stop </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:54 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/18/2026 01:08:33 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-55</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371330</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner: Planner will plan waypoints around a map shape obstacle and stop</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>Objective:<br> • Verifies that when there is a obstacle shape on the map and a path is planned through the obstacle on the fairway shape that the mower will stop.<br> <br> Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Path plans are created around or that avoid the obstacle shape.<br> • Simulator is located withing the area coverage map shape.<br> <br> Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL/HIL.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius app installed and running with latest version of "AreaCoverageLibraries" integrated<br> • Map is published in mobius.<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Map Loaded - SmallMowingMap.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Map.<br> • Obstacle on map.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Load a map and assign a waypoint drive, Map loaded and waypoint created<br>2: Set a new waypoint through an obstacle on a fairway, New waypoint is created through an obstacle and assigned<br>3: Assign Plan and Start Run, Mower will Conditional stop and be at 0 velocity</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-941</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-56 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213336"> Mobius: Planner: Action points added and based on area-coverage map boundary </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:55 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/29/2026 01:27:12 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-56</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371331</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner: Action points added and based on area-coverage map boundary</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that action points are automatically generated based on the area-coverage map shape boundary, rather than the starting point of the end-of-row turn.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius Planner behavior when generating action points for area-coverage maps.<br> • Validation that irregular or non-rectangular map boundaries correctly produce action-point placement aligned to the boundary.<br> • Applies to SIL, HIL, and ME-HIL environments where area-coverage planning is supported.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • The latest Mobius Server, Mobius Client, and VCU SIL/HIL builds are installed and compatible with updated area-coverage planning logic.<br> • The map shape boundary is fully enclosed within a drivable area, as required for this feature to function.<br> • The provided test map (.json) is correctly formatted and compatible with Mobius Planner.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>Preconditions:<br> • Mobius app installed and running with latest version of "AreaCoverageLibraries" integrated<br> • Mobius Server and Client are running.<br> • Simulator is powered on, checked in, and located within the area-coverage map boundary.<br> • Implement is created and attached to the Simulator.</p> <p>• Mower is checked into Mobius and ready for assignment<br> <br> Environment:<br> • Map Loaded and published - SmallMowingMap.<br> • Simulator positioned inside the test map's area-coverage boundary.<br> • Planning libraries and AreaCoverageLibraries are up to date.<br> <br> Equipment:<br> • Latest VCU SIL/HIL build or Simulator build capable of executing area-coverage planning.<br> • One checked-in simulated mower with an attached implement.<br> <br> Test Data:<br> • Map: SmallMowingMap.<br> • Expected automatic action-point locations along the map shape boundary.</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Set Lane Generation&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set Boundary Lap Generation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set Swath Generation&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Set Swath Connection&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Add Planned Action Point&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Finalize Plan and Assign, • Lane Gen set to:&amp;nbsp;laneBuffer: Feet(4.92),&lt;br /&gt;<br>laneOutsideDistance: Feet(4.59)&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;• Boundary Lap Gen set to:&amp;nbsp;numberOfLaps: 1,&lt;br /&gt;<br>direction: CleanupLapDirection.Any,&lt;br /&gt;<br>order: CleanupOrdering.InnerFirstOuterLast,&lt;br /&gt;<br>velocity: MilesPerHour(4),&lt;br /&gt;<br>overlap: Feet(9.84),&lt;br /&gt;<br>targetMaxDeviation: Feet(0.1),&lt;br /&gt;<br>allowedMaxDeviation: Feet(0.33),&lt;br /&gt;<br>approachBoundaryGrow: Feet(0.66),&lt;br /&gt;<br>approachBoundaryShrink: Feet(1.31)&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;• Swath Gen set to:&amp;nbsp;guidanceLineName: null,&lt;br /&gt;<br>angle: double.NaN,&lt;br /&gt;<br>velocity: MilesPerHour(6)&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;• Swath Connection set to:&amp;nbsp;connectionPattern: ConnectionPattern.Striped,&lt;br /&gt;<br>velocity: MilesPerHour(3),&lt;br /&gt;<br>allowCrossing: false,&lt;br /&gt;<br>allowPatching: true,&lt;br /&gt;<br>allowMultiPointTurns: true,&lt;br /&gt;<br>reverseSegmentMaxLength: Feet(13.12),&lt;br /&gt;<br>reverseSegmentPenalty: Feet(20),&lt;br /&gt;<br>progressiveOffset: Feet(0.98),&lt;br /&gt;<br>lanelessRowConnectionWeight: 0,&lt;br /&gt;<br>scoreTrimMultiplier: Feet(32.81),&lt;br /&gt;<br>extension: Feet(3.28)&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;• Added planned action point&amp;nbsp;lookahead: Feet(10.5)&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;• Finalize and Assign<br>2: Set Offline planning details, Verify Expected action points in the .json file (test is source of expected action data points</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Failed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
