  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-57 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213337"> Mobius: Planning: Mower executes area coverage plan with action points </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:55 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/09/2026 03:02:35 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-57</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371332</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planning: Mower executes area coverage plan with action points</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the mower successfully executes an area-coverage plan containing action points that control PTO on/off and reel lower/raise operations during plan execution.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of Mobius Planner and Vehicle Control Unit when executing area-coverage plans that include operational action points.<br> • Validation that the mower performs the correct implement actions (PTO and reel states) when reaching each action point along the plan path.<br> • Applies to SIL, HIL, and ME-HIL environments supporting action-point execution logic.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Latest Mobius Server, Mobius Client, and VCU SIL/HIL builds support action-point-driven PTO and reel commands.<br> • The area-coverage map includes valid action points embedded in the planned path.<br> • The mower or simulator is capable of executing implement commands and reporting implement state changes.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Server and Client installed and running with latest AreaCoverageLibraries integrated.<br> • Mower or Simulator is checked in, powered on, and ready for plan execution.<br> • Mobius map is created, published, and includes an area-coverage shape with defined action points.<br> • Simulator or mower is positioned within the area-coverage map boundary.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Map loaded and published in Mobius (Area-Coverage plan containing action points): <br> • Environment supports implement operations (PTO and reel actuation).<br> • Planning libraries are up to date.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Latest VCU SIL/HIL build or Simulator build supporting implement commands.<br> • One checked-in mower or simulator with an attached implement capable of PTO and reel actions.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Area-coverage map with embedded action points: SmallMowingMap<br> • Expected implement behaviors:<br> • PTO: On → Off sequences<br> • Reels: Lower → Raise sequences</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create plan and assign, Plan is created and assigned<br>2: Run plan and verify the plan is being executed, Mower is executing assigned plan<br>3: Pause the plan, Verify Deck Controller State is UP&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Verify PTO Controller State is Off<br>4: Clear Assignments, Assignment is removed&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;PTO Controller State is Off</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1179</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-58 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213338"> Mobius: Planner: Area-coverage mower executes alternating row direction </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:55 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/12/2026 01:04:30 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-58</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371333</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner: Area-coverage mower executes alternating row direction</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the area-coverage planner generates mowing rows such that every other row is mowed in the opposite direction, ensuring alternating mowing patterns across the field.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of Mobius Planner when generating alternating-direction coverage rows for mowing.<br> • Validation that the coverage pattern does not require sequential left-to-right or right-to-left field traversal; only alternating direction between rows is required.<br> • Applies to SIL, HIL, ME-HIL, and real mower testing environments that support area-coverage planning.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • The latest Mobius Server, Mobius Client, and VCU SIL/HIL builds support alternating-direction area-coverage planning.<br> • The area-coverage map shape used for the test is a real golf-course fairway and is compatible with Mobius Planner.<br> • The mower or simulator is equipped with an implement capable of mowing behavior and reporting coverage execution states.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Server and Client installed, connected, and running.<br> • Simulator or real mower is powered on, checked in, and ready for plan execution.<br> • Mobius map is created, published, and includes an area-coverage shape representing a real fairway.<br> • Mower implement is created and attached to the vehicle (8 ft width preferred).<br><br>Environment:<br> • Map loaded and published in Mobius with a real fairway area-coverage shape.<br> • Planner libraries and AreaCoverageLibraries up to date.<br> • Environment supports execution or simulation of mowing coverage patterns.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Latest VCU SIL/HIL build or Simulator build capable of running alternating-direction area-coverage plans.<br> • One mower or simulator with an attached mowing implement (8 ft preferred).<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Area-coverage plan generated from the fairway map shape.<br> • Expected pattern: Each subsequent row alternates mowing direction (Alternating Row direction on adjacent swaths).</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create plan, New Plan is created that contains alt directions<br>2: Assign new plan, New Plan is assigned<br>3: Begin running the new and assigned plan, The mower is running the new plan<br>4: Mower running the plan, Heading alternates direction for adjacent swaths</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1209</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-59 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213339"> Mobius: Planner: Dynamic area-coverage action points for reel engagement </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:55 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/12/2026 07:21:33 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-59</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371334</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner: Dynamic area-coverage action points for reel engagement</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the area-coverage planner generates mowing rows such that every other row is mowed in the opposite direction, ensuring alternating mowing patterns across the field.<br>Verify that during area-coverage planning, action points are automatically placed to control reel engagement and disengagement, and that the mower correctly performs dynamic speed adjustments when crossing these action points.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of Mobius Planner when generating dynamic action points for reel operations within area-coverage plans.<br> • Validation that:<br> • The mower slows to the lowest configured speed upon crossing an action point.<br> • The mower maintains the lowest speed for the length of the vehicle.<br> • After completing the vehicle-length segment, the mower returns to the planned segment speed.<br> • Applies to SIL, HIL, ME-HIL, and Simulator-based environments that support dynamic action-point behavior.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Latest Mobius Server, Mobius Client, and VCU SIL/HIL builds support dynamic speed transitions triggered by action points.<br> • Area-coverage map shape contains valid boundaries and is compatible with reel-based implement operations.<br> • Swath extensions are applied at their maximum allowable distance within the drivable area.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Fairway mower or Simulator is checked in, powered on, and available in Mobius.<br> • Map with an Area-Coverage Shape is uploaded and published in Mobius.<br> • Swath Extensions are configured to the largest allowable distance within the drivable area.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Area-coverage plan generated from the selected fairway or custom shape.<br> • Dynamic action-point behavior enabled within Planner and VCU builds.<br> • Planner libraries and AreaCoverageLibraries up to date.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Latest VCU SIL/HIL or Simulator build supporting dynamic action points and speed transitions.<br> • One mower or simulator with an attached implement capable of reel operations.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Area-coverage map with dynamic action points generated.<br> • Expected behaviors:<br> • Reel engage/disengage action points appear along the plan.<br> • Vehicle slows to lowest speed after crossing each action point.<br> • Vehicle resumes segment speed after traveling the length of the vehicle.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create new plan and assign, New plan is created and assigned<br>2: Begin running plan with mower, Mower starts running the plan<br>3: Check PTO and Deck Values for expected states, PTO should be 1&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Deck value should be 1&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Mower speed should be at least 3kph<br>4: Verify:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;First Deck Value&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;First PTO Value&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Second Deck Value, First Deck Value should be 0&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;First PTO Value should be 1&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Second Deck Value should be 1&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;KPH should be 4</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1367</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-60 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213340"> VCU: VCU initiates warning period before automated engine start after image confirmation. </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:55 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/21/2026 01:41:17 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-60</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371335</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: VCU initiates warning period before automated engine start after image confirmation.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verifies that once the supervisor confirms the hazard zone is free of obstacles, the machine initiates the required warning period (AudioVisualState:TealSolidAmberSlowAudioA) before the automated engine start sequence begins.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of the VCU and Mobius system when obstacle detection requires Local confirmation.<br> • Validation that the warning period (AudioVisualState:TealSolidAmberSlowAudioA) is triggered after image confirmation and before engine start.<br> • Applies to SIL, HIL, ME-HIL, and real-vehicle environments that support automated engine start with pre-start safety behaviors.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Latest Mobius Server, Mobius Client, and VCU builds support image confirmation workflows and the associated warning period sequence.<br> • Audio, beacon, and visual indicators corresponding to TealSolidAmberSlowAudioA are functional and properly mapped in the VCU.<br> • Obstacle detection system is operational and capable of producing events requiring Local confirmation.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mower or simulator checked into Mobius and powered on.<br> • Safe testing environment established for pre-start engine behavior.<br> • Obstacle detection system configured and able to request Local confirmation.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Mobius connected to the vehicle with communication channels available for hazard confirmation and engine-start commands.<br> • Audio/visual alert systems active and capable of presenting TealSolidAmberSlowAudioA.<br> • System in a state where automated engine start is permitted once all preconditions and confirmations are satisfied.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Latest VCU SIL/HIL build or real mower supporting the automated start warning sequence.<br> • Working beacon and audible alarm system (real or simulated).<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Hazard-zone detection requiring Local confirmation.<br> • Expected audio-visual behavior: AudioVisualState: TealSolidAmberSlowAudioA initiated before the engine start.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Toggle Manual to Autonomous &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Clear Local Confirmation<br>2: Power Engine On, Expect AudioVisualState.TealSolidAmberSlowAudioA&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;PropulsionState.Ready</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1535</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
