  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-91 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213371"> VCU: Prevent Deck Control Error during exit-transport; mower must fully stop and complete reel lift before continuing </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:57 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/09/2026 02:11:03 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-91</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371366</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Prevent Deck Control Error during exit-transport; mower must fully stop and complete reel lift before continuing</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that during exit transport mode, the mower fully stops, completes the reel-lift operation, and only then continues motion-ensuring no Deck Control Error is triggered while the reels transition from crosscut to transport.<br> • Confirm that both the initial downward reel action (beginning of the fairway) and the final upward reel action (end of the fairway) complete cleanly without state-mismatch errors.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of the VCU deck-control subsystem during:<br> • Initial "reels-down" action when starting the fairway<br> • Final "reels-up to transport" action during exit transport mode<br> • Validation that:<br> • Mower stops fully before exit-transport reel movement<br> • Reel movement fully completes prior to motion resumption<br> • No Deck Control Error appears during either the initial or final reel transitions<br> • Applies to real-mower testing only (sim cannot reproduce the timing/motion mismatch).<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • VCU version b4fc7558eb or later includes logic ensuring exit-transport actions occur while the mower is stationary.<br> • Reel-position CAN feedback accurately reports movement and completion state.<br> • Mobius UI correctly displays reel transitions and error states.<br> • Fairway plan includes valid action points for reel lowering and raising.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Real mower connected and operational.<br> • Mobius Server and Mobius Client running.<br> • VCU firmware version b4fc7558eb (or under test) installed.<br> • Fairway ACP created containing:<br> • Reels-down action at start<br> • Reels-up (transport) action at end<br><br>Environment:<br> • Outdoor or controlled mowing environment.<br> • Real-time CAN feedback and deck-control logic active.<br> • Logging enabled for implement state, motion state, and deck-control errors.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower with working reel actuators and PTU system.<br> • Mobius Client for observing actions, errors, and mower behavior.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Area Coverage Plan with a cleanup lap and final transport action.<br> • Expected behavior:<br> • At start of fairway:<br> • Mower lowers reels from transport → crosscut<br> • No Deck Control Error appears<br> • At final action point:<br> • Mower comes to a complete stop<br> • Reels raise from crosscut → transport<br> • Action fully completes before the mower moves again<br> • No Deck Control Error is thrown</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create, assign plan, and run<br>verify: On mission complete Deck Value is 0 or UP, Expected: On compleed execution of a plan, Deck is up in transport mode position</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1927</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-92 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213372"> Mobius: Offline Planner supports creation of 2-cleanup-lap plans (and configurable cleanup-lap counts) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:57 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:43:47 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-92</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371367</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Offline Planner supports creation of 2-cleanup-lap plans (and configurable cleanup-lap counts)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the Mobius Offline Planner allows the user to create an Area Coverage Plan (ACP) with exactly 2 cleanup laps, and more broadly, that the Number of Laps parameter correctly determines how many cleanup laps are generated.<br> • Confirm that the plan preview and the resulting stored plan accurately reflect the selected number of boundary laps.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of the Offline Planner during boundary-lap generation.<br> • Validation that:<br> • Setting "Number of Laps =3D 2" produces a 2-cleanup-lap plan.<br> • Setting "Number of Laps &gt; 2" produces a plan with the exact number of laps specified.<br> • Default lane-generation and other wizard steps do not alter lap count.<br> • Applies to Mobius Client Offline Planner for both simulated and real mower assets.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Mobius Offline Planner supports multi-lap cleanup generation.<br> • Fairway shapes include valid geometry for boundary-lap creation.<br> • User interface correctly displays lap count and plan structure after generation.<br> • Simulated and real mowers can be used as selectable assets.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • User has a physical or simulated mower placed adjacent to a fairway.<br> • User is viewing the Plan Organizer for that fairway in Mobius.<br> • Offline Planner feature enabled and accessible.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Offline Planner interface active.<br> • Fairway selected for new plan generation.<br> • Successful navigation through Planner steps (Asset Selection → Lane Generation → Boundary Lap Generation → Review).<br> • Mobius Client capable of rendering cleanup-lap paths.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Client with Offline Planner capability.<br> • Either a real mower or simulator registered as an asset.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Fairway geometry and associated Offline Planner parameters.<br> • Expected behavior:<br> • With "Number of Laps =3D 2":<br> • Offline Planner outputs a plan with exactly two cleanup laps.<br> • With "Number of Laps &gt; 2":<br> • Offline Planner outputs a plan with the exact number of cleanup laps selected.<br> • Plan appears correctly in the plan list and can be previewed.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create a two clean up lap plan, assign plan<br>verify: Plan has two clean up laps, Expected: Plan has two clean up laps</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1929</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-93 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213373"> Mobius: Prevent invalid “Segment Unknown” errors during shallow-angle turn segments </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:57 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:42:01 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-93</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371368</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Prevent invalid “Segment Unknown” errors during shallow-angle turn segments</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the system no longer produces invalid "Current Segment Unknown" errors during mowing, specifically in cases where the mower exits a fairway at a shallow angle and re-enters the fairway via an asymmetric turn arc.<br> • Confirm that shallow-angle turn segments are generated cleanly, without gaps, discontinuities, or geometry artifacts that cause the VCU to lose track of the current path segment.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Behavior of Mobius Planner and the VCU's segment-tracking logic during complex turn geometries.<br> • Validation that:<br> • Shallow-angle turns and long-leg/short-leg turn arcs do not cause breakpoints or disconnected path geometry.<br> • Mobius correctly identifies the current segment throughout the maneuver.<br> • No invalid Segment Unknown errors are raised during mowing.<br> • Planner output is continuous and logically connected at the path-node level.<br> • Applies to SIL, HIL, ME-HIL, simulator, and real-mower tests.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Mobius Planner has been updated to reduce or eliminate path-segment discontinuities around shallow-angle approaches.<br> • VCU firmware includes improved logic for segment indexing, tolerance windows, or turn-arc interpolation.<br> • Sim environment reliably reproduces segment-tracking behavior.<br> • "Segment Unknown" errors are unintended artifacts, not legitimate safety stops.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Server and Client running.<br> • Simulator connected or real mower available.<br> • A fairway exists where a planned turn arc includes one leg significantly longer than the other (shallow-angle exit and re-entry).<br> • Plan either created in Mobius or loaded from existing plans that exhibit this geometry.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Mobius Client able to visualize planned paths and turn arcs.<br> • Planner libraries updated to IRD128-1702 fixes.<br> • Segment-tracking telemetry available during execution (optional but helpful).<br> • No preexisting errors active on the mower or sim.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Simulator or real mower capable of executing an ACP.<br> • Latest VCU firmware under investigation for segment-tracking improvements.<br> • Mobius Client for monitoring segment status.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • ACP containing:<br> • A shallow-angle departure from the fairway,<br> • An asymmetric turn arc (long outbound, short return or vice versa).<br> • Expected behavior:<br> • Plan executes with no breaks or discontinuities in the turn path.<br> • Mower follows the turn arc without causing "Current Segment Unknown."<br> • No invalid Segment Unknown errors appear in Mobius UI or logs.<br> • Mower completes the turn and continues mowing normally.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create plan, assign, and begin executing the plan<br>verify: that there are no invalid Segment Unknow errors, Expected: Mower completes planned path and Segment Unknown does not stop operations</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1938</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-94 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213374"> VCU: Reels fail to lower after 3-pt turns with reverse due to incorrect distance calculation </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:57 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/06/2026 01:27:09 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-94</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371369</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Reels fail to lower after 3-pt turns with reverse due to incorrect distance calculation</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that during 3-point turns, the mower consistently lifts the reels during the reverse segment and lowers them again at the appropriate point when re-entering the fairway or crossing the "reels down" action point.<br> • Validate that the updated logic (switching from velocity-based to speed-based distance evaluation) resolves cases where the mower fails to lower the reels due to miscalculated reverse-segment distance.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Covers reel-control behavior during complex turn maneuvers, specifically 3-pt turns where the mower transitions between forward and reverse movement.<br> • Ensures correct handling of:<br> • Reverse-segment distance accumulation,<br> • Action point execution,<br> • Reel position state transitions (Transport ↔ Crosscut).<br> • Applies to real mower and SIM/HIL environments when reel-control logic is active.<br> • Validation focuses on consistency and correctness across all 3-pt turns within an ACP.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Updated VCU logic is deployed where speed (not velocity vector) is used for turn-segment distance calculations.<br> • Action points exist in the plan where reel lowering should occur after reverse segments.<br> • Test fairways such as Preston Country Club contain known problematic 3-pt turns for regression confirmation.<br> • Mower or simulator is capable of reporting reel state changes accurately.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Server and Client running with current Planner libraries.<br> • Real mower or simulator checked in and operational.<br> • A plan is created that includes at least one tight 3-pt turn on a fairway.<br> • Implement attached and capable of reel up/down actuation.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Area-coverage plan with one or more 3-pt turns, ideally on fairways where issues are known to repeat (e.g., Preston test maps).<br> • Normal reel-operation parameters active (no overrides disabling deck movement).<br> • Logging enabled to capture reel commands (down/up), reverse motion, and distance calculations.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower preferred (SIM acceptable if reel logic is implemented).<br> • Latest VCU firmware under test.<br> • Mobius Client for monitoring motion, reel state, and action point execution.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • ACP with at least one 3-pt turn involving:<br> • A reverse segment,<br> • A subsequent forward re-entry onto the fairway.<br> • Expected behavior:<br> • Reels lift during reverse.<br> • Reels lower when returning to the fairway or when reaching the correct action point.<br> • No missed reel-down events after reverse segments.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create plan, assign, and begin executing the plan<br>verify: that after a 3-point turn with reverse that the reels lowered on the begining of the next swath, Expected: Reels lower after 3-point turn with reverse</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Failed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-1939</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
