  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-111 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213391"> Mobius: Planner Error Highlighting — Display Offending Segments in Red </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:58 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:33:28 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-111</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371386</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner Error Highlighting — Display Offending Segments in Red</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that when the planner encounters an error during plan creation, the exact segment(s) responsible for the failure are highlighted in red on the Offline Planner map.<br> • Ensure that selecting an error in the Error Panel automatically focuses on and displays the problematic geometry.<br> • Confirm that all error text shown in Mobius is properly localized.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Offline Planner error-handling and visualization.<br> • Validation includes:<br> • Error detection during lane, swath, or boundary lap generation,<br> • Highlighting of offending segments when errors occur,<br> • Error selection behavior in the Error Panel,<br> • Localization of error text in the UI.<br> • Applies to any fairway where obstacles, shape boundaries, or geometric constraints cause planning failures.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • The build includes IRD128-1376 enhancements for error visualization.<br> • Planner is capable of identifying specific failing segments rather than failing silently or generically.<br> • Error Panel supports selecting individual errors and triggering visual highlighting.<br> • Localization files are up to date for displayed error text.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Client running with access to the Offline Planner.<br> • Simulator connected (simply required for enabling the planning workflow).<br> • A fairway selected that is known to produce planning errors (e.g., obstacles too close to area coverage region).<br> • Planner configured to surface validation errors during plan generation.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Offline Planner with a fairway containing problem geometry.<br> • Error Panel visible when errors occur.<br> • Visualization layer supports highlighting segments in red.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Mobius Server.<br> • Simulator (or real mower, not required for this test).<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Fairway with obstacles or unplannable constraints.<br> • Expected behavior:<br> • When an error occurs, the associated segment(s) are highlighted in red on the plan view.<br> • Selecting the error in the Error Panel re-centers or reveals the highlighted segment(s).<br> • Error messages are localized as expected.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Duplicate Active Map and Publish with an obstacle shape<br>Verify planner posted an error for the segment that has an issue, Expect planner errors for segments that have issues</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2053</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-112 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213392"> Mobius Server: Generates Additional Intersection Sets for Off-Path and Hazard-Zone Scenarios </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:58 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:32:24 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-112</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371387</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius Server: Generates Additional Intersection Sets for Off-Path and Hazard-Zone Scenarios</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that Mobius generates and provides the Planner with the newly required intersection sets that support enhanced off-path and hazard-zone validation.<br> • Confirm that Mobius correctly computes and sends the following intersection-set configurations:<br> • Full off-path error + hazard zone,<br> • Slimmed-down off-path error,<br> • No hazard-zone buffer intersection set.<br> • Ensure that plans generated in these scenarios behave correctly and that the planner receives accurate intersection geometries for validation.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Interaction between Mobius map geometry, intersection computation, and the Planner's validation logic.<br> • Includes map editing, plan generation, connect-swath intersection visualization, and running the final plan.<br> • Applicable to Offline Planner and real-time plan execution (SIM or mower).<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Mobius build contains IRD128-2235 changes for expanded intersection-set generation.<br> • Planner expects and consumes all three intersection-set configurations.<br> • Fairway boundary, obstacle geometry, and buffer distances are calculated consistently.<br> • Simulator accurately reflects off-path slowdown behavior but does not trigger invalid hazard checks.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Server and Client running and connected.<br> • Simulator available and checked in.<br> • Fairway map available for editing.<br> • Planner capable of generating errors and highlights based on intersection sets.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Map Editor with obstacle/bunker creation enabled.<br> • Offline Planner with Connect Swaths visualization and error reporting.<br> • Logging available for intersection-set data sent to Planner.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Simulator (real mower optional).<br> • Map with obstacle correctly placed near a fairway edge (~2 ft or less).<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Fairway with obstacle close enough to trigger intersection warnings.<br> • Intersection sets expected:<br> • Full off-path + hazard zone,<br> • Slimmed-down off-path only,<br> • No hazard-zone buffer.<br><br>Expected Behavior:<br> • Map publishes successfully and obstacle appears in Command tab.<br> • Offline Planner highlights swaths intersecting or nearing obstacle boundary and displays an error.<br> • Planner uses intersection sets provided by Mobius for validation.<br> • Running the plan:<br> • Mower completes the plan without invalid errors.<br> • Mower may slow near the obstacle but does not leave drivable area.<br> • No unexpected hazard or off-path violations occur.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Creat plan with an obstacle and verify plan was successful<br>Start execution of the plan<br>Verify IntersectionSetType HazardlessSlim &amp;amp; IntersectionSetType Hazardless, Expect Intersections are created as expected</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2056</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-113 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213393"> Mobius: Planner: Add Action Points for Updated Off-Path Error Based on Intersection Sets </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:58 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/25/2026 01:04:09 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-113</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371388</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner: Add Action Points for Updated Off-Path Error Based on Intersection Sets</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that action points are automatically added to the plan when off-path error limits change based on the intersection set selected by the planner.<br> • Confirm that updated off-path error values result in new or adjusted action-point placement.<br> • Ensure the vehicle uses the updated off-path error configuration to correctly navigate around obstacles or boundaries.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Interaction between Offline Planning, VCU configuration values, and planner-generated action points.<br> • Includes observation of how changing "Maximum Allowed Off Path Error" affects plan geometry and action-point positions.<br> • Applies to Offline Planner workflows where intersection sets influence action-point generation.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Mobius build includes IRD128-2238 updates for off-path error intersection-set functionality.<br> • Planner recalculates path geometry and action points when off-path limits are modified.<br> • VCU configuration correctly propagates updated off-path thresholds into planning.<br> • Simulator behavior reflects the updated plan but does not need to execute the full plan for validation.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Server and Client running and connected.<br> • Offline Planner available with at least one fairway suitable for planning.<br> • VCU configuration tab accessible for modifying "Maximum Allowed Off Path Error."<br> • Planner capable of generating action points and rendering changes based on configuration updates.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Offline Planning interface with Connect Swaths and action-point visualization enabled.<br> • VCU configuration accessible via Settings → Vehicle → Configuration.<br> • Logging available to review plan differences before and after threshold changes.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Mobius Server.<br> • Simulator (or mower; simulator is sufficient).<br><br>Test Data:<br> • A fairway that produces multiple action points.<br> • Two planning runs:<br> • one using the default off-path error value,<br> • one after modifying the "Maximum Allowed Off Path Error."</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Creat plan and assign<br>Start execution of the plan<br>Verify assignments with intersection sets, Expect intersection sets to be in the plan</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2059</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-114 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213394"> Mobius: Server Telemetry — MTTI &amp; MTTR Calculation and Reporting </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:59 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/19/2026 01:01:22 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-114</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371389</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Server Telemetry — MTTI &amp; MTTR Calculation and Reporting</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the VCU calculates and reports MTTI (Mean Time To Intervention) and MTTR (Mean Time To Recovery) using new telemetry fields.<br> • Confirm that Mobius exposes gauges for cumulative operational durations and intervention metrics.<br> • Ensure that MTTI and MTTR values update correctly during normal operation, intervention events, and recovery.<br><br>Scope:<br> • VCU telemetry generation and Mobius gauge display.<br> • Calculation of cumulative durations (power-on, auto-mode, runtime, downtime).<br> • Tracking intervention-causing errors and transition counts.<br> • Applicable only to real mower hardware equipped with updated VCU firmware supporting these metrics.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • VCU firmware includes IRD128-2372 telemetry fields for MTTI, MTTR, cumulative durations, and intervention counts.<br> • Mobius Client supports displaying new telemetry gauges.<br> • Image confirmation is still used for clearing estops at the time of this test.<br> • Required data is logged and available for Power BI reporting.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Real mower available and running VCU firmware with MTTI/MTTR support.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client connected to the mower.<br> • Fairway plan available for execution.<br> • Telemetry panel configured to display new gauges (MTTI, MTTR, cumulative durations, intervention counts).<br><br>Environment:<br> • Live operational fairway or controlled testing environment.<br> • Stable wireless or network connection between mower and Mobius Client.<br> • Logging enabled to capture telemetry changes during estop events and recovery.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower with updated VCU firmware.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client capable of rendering telemetry gauges.<br> • Timing device (stopwatch or equivalent) for manual MTTR comparison.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • A normal mowing plan.<br> • Telemetry fields:<br> • cumulative power-on duration<br> • cumulative auto-mode duration<br> • cumulative runtime duration<br> • cumulative downtime duration<br> • total required intervention count<br> • run-state to stop-state transitions<br> • intervention-causing error codes (#1 through #10)<br> • MTTI and MTTR calculated fields<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Mobius displays gauges for MTTI, MTTR, and all cumulative telemetry fields after enabling them.<br> • MTTR increases to represent the time between estop activation and clearing/recovery, matching the manually measured duration.<br> • MTTI reflects average runtime between interventions once the plan completes.<br> • Intervention-causing error codes populate according to VCU logs.<br> • MTTI &gt; MTTR under normal mowing conditions unless recovery time exceeds active mowing time for that mission segment.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Creat plan, Assign and execute the plan<br>Adjust the map and re-publish with the obstacle updates<br>Begin execution of the plan <br>Verify gather and verify that the MTTR/MTTI exists in the executation data from MeanTimeToIntervention Telemetry object, Expect that MTTI exists</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
