  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-115 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213395"> Mobius: Telemetry Velocity Calculation Enhancements for Mowing &amp; Driving Modes </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:03:59 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/12/2026 07:22:56 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-115</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371390</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Telemetry Velocity Calculation Enhancements for Mowing &amp; Driving Modes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that new velocity-related telemetry items are added and correctly reported in Mobius, including velocity controller average error and updated mowing/overall velocity metrics.<br> • Confirm that mowing velocity statistics are calculated only during mowing conditions (reels down, PTO on, speed above stopped threshold).<br> • Validate that overall velocity statistics are calculated any time the mower is in autonomous mode and moving above the stop threshold.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Telemetry reporting from VCU to Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Calculation of mowing-specific and overall velocity metrics, including averages and standard deviations.<br> • Applicable only to real mower hardware running updated VCU code for IRD128-2407.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • VCU firmware includes changes for the following velocity telemetry items:<br> • velocity controller average error<br> • mowing velocity averages and standard deviations<br> • path segment velocity error metrics<br> • overall velocity averages and standard deviations<br> • Mobius Desktop Client supports displaying these new telemetry fields as gauges.<br> • The mower is able to run a full or partial plan to generate meaningful telemetry samples.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Real mower with IRD128-2407 firmware updates deployed.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client connected to the mower.<br> • A fairway plan available for execution to produce mowing and non-mowing velocity data.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Real-world mowing environment with typical fairway geometry.<br> • Telemetry panel configured to display all new velocity metrics.<br> • Stable communication between mower and Mobius Desktop Client.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower with updated VCU velocity calculation firmware.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client capable of rendering telemetry gauges.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Telemetry items under test:<br> • velocity controller average error<br> • mowing average speed<br> • mowing velocity controller error (avg &amp; std dev)<br> • mowing path-segment velocity error (avg &amp; std dev)<br> • segment error (movement only)<br> • overall average driving speed<br> • overall velocity controller error (avg &amp; std dev)<br> • overall path-segment velocity error (avg &amp; std dev)<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Mobius displays gauges for all new velocity telemetry items once added.<br> • Mowing velocity metrics update only when reels are down, PTO is on, and mower is moving above the stopping threshold.<br> • Overall velocity metrics update whenever the mower is in autonomous mode and moving above the stop threshold.<br> • Mean velocities differ depending on fairway:<br> • Small/tight fairways produce lower mean speeds,<br> • Long straight fairways produce higher means but never equal absolute top speed, since metrics are averaged over time.<br> • Velocity controller error and path-segment velocity error statistics update only when the mower is moving, and correctly reflect mowing vs. non-mowing conditions.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Creat plan, Assign and execute the plan<br>Verify the following telemetry items values: <br> DriveSpeedMean<br> MowSpeedMean<br> MowVelocityControllerErrorMean<br> MowVelocityControllerErrorStdDev<br> MowSegmentVelocityErrorMean<br> MowSegmentVelocityErrorStdDev, Expect the values for each telemetry item:</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2066</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-116 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213396"> Mobius: VCU gets updated DKS Parameter for 6 MPH Mowing Performance </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">03/09/2026 02:56:53 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-116</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371391</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: VCU gets updated DKS Parameter for 6 MPH Mowing Performance</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that DKS parameters are updated to support achieving a consistent 6 MPH mowing speed as required by GNC guidance.<br> • Confirm that modifying Pace.throttlePID.Kp and Pace.throttlePID.Ki results in improved throttle control and stable target-speed performance.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Validation of DKS parameter updates related to throttle PID tuning.<br> • Applies to real mower operation under autonomous control while executing a plan.<br> • Includes speed-gauge observation within Mobius Desktop.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • VCU firmware version 3.4 or higher is installed.<br> • The mower's throttle-control system responds directly to updates in Pace.throttlePID parameters.<br> • Mobius reflects updated parameters immediately when saved in DKS.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Real mower available and functioning.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client connected to the mower.<br> • VCU running firmware version ≥ 3.4.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Outdoor or controlled mowing area where target speeds can be safely tested.<br> • Stable connection between mower and Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Speed gauge visible in Mobius during plan execution.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower with active DKS configuration access.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • DKS values to update:<br> • Pace.throttlePID.Kp =3D 6.5<br> • Pace.throttlePID.Ki =3D 2.25<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Updated DKS parameters save successfully.<br> • Mower executes the plan and accelerates without oscillation or undershoot.<br> • Speed gauge in Mobius shows the mower consistently achieving 6 MPH during straight segments.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Set DKS settings for the mower assigned. Change the settings Pace.throttlePID.Kp to 6.5 and Pace.throttlePID.Ki to 2.25.<br>Run the mower through a plan.<br>Verify the speed gauge in Mobius. Mower should be consistently at 6 MPH., Expect the mower should be able to consistently hit 6 MPH.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2073</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
