  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-119 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213399"> VCU: Update Local Confirmation Timeout to 60 Seconds &amp; Change Occlusion Severity to Hard Estop (IRD128-2519) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:37:42 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-119</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371394</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Update Local Confirmation Timeout to 60 Seconds &amp; Change Occlusion Severity to Hard Estop (IRD128-2519)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the Local Confirmation timeout has been updated to 60 seconds.<br> • Validate that occlusion-zone violations now trigger a hard estop rather than a soft hazard response.<br> • Confirm that clearing estop behaves correctly relative to the new timeout duration.<br><br>Scope:<br> • VCU local-confirmation logic and estop severity handling.<br> • Applies to both sim and real mower behavior validating timeout enforcement.<br> • Includes verifying Auto/Manual toggle and estop-clear interactions relative to the 60-second window.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • IRD128-2519 firmware changes are deployed on the mower or simulator.<br> • VCU now enforces a 60-second Local Confirmation timeout.<br> • Occlusion-zone violations are classified as hard estop conditions.<br> • Mobius UI correctly reports estop states and transitions.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client connected to a real mower or simulator.<br> • Updated VCU firmware including the modified timeout and estop logic.<br> • Mower in a state where Auto/Manual toggling and estop clearing can be performed safely.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Mobius Desktop with stable telemetry/command communication.<br> • Test environment where repeated estop transitions pose no safety risk.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower or simulator with IRD128-2519 firmware.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client with visibility into estop states.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Local confirmation timeout value: 60 seconds.<br> • Estop condition expected: Hard estop (0xC708) triggered by occlusion violation.<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Auto/Manual toggle momentarily loads the mower then correctly returns it to a hard estop state.<br> • Clearing estop after 60 seconds produces no effect.<br> • Clearing estop before 60 seconds results in the mower exiting estop and loading normally.<br> • Estop severity is always hard estop when occlusion logic is triggered.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Toggle mower to Autonomous mode<br>Clear Local Confirmation and wait for time out, Verify that the mower is e-stopped<br>Expecct that the is e-stopped and no longer Occlusion zone violated</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2098</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-120 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213400"> VCU: Logging Add raiseCutUnitSwitch Debug Output to VCU Logs (IRD128-2559) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:35:34 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-120</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371395</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Logging Add raiseCutUnitSwitch Debug Output to VCU Logs (IRD128-2559)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that raiseCutUnitSwitch state-change debugging is now logged by the VCU.<br> • Confirm that reel up/down transitions produce readable, timestamped debug entries in the VCU console.<br> • Ensure the log output occurs only when reels transition and does not duplicate both up and down messages simultaneously.<br><br>Scope:<br> • VCU logging subsystem and console output formatting.<br> • Reel-control command transitions during mowing operations.<br> • Applies only to real hardware; simulator does not generate this telemetry or log state.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • The mower is running VCU firmware with IRD128-2559 integrated.<br> • Reel-control logic updates generate debug lines on state changes (Down → Up, Up → Down).<br> • VCU console access is available through Mobius Desktop.<br> • CutSwitchState transitions occur during normal mowing (action points, headlands, or turns).<br><br>Setup:<br>Preconditions:<br> • Real mower running 3.5+ release harness with IRD128-2559 logging changes.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client connected to mower.<br> • Ability to open and monitor VCU console during mowing.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions: • Real mower running 3.5+ release harness with IRD128-2559 logging changes. • Mobius Desktop Client connected to mower. • Ability to open and monitor VCU console during mowing. Environment: • Outdoor or indoor controlled mowing environment where a plan can be executed. • Reliable CAN bus and telemetry communication. Equipment: • Real mower with updated VCU firmware. • Mobius Desktop Client with VCU console window available. Test Data: • Expected debug message pattern: ReelControl::CutSwitchState change Off/On -&gt; Down/Up • CutSwitchState should show one transition per command, not paired messages. Expected behavior: • As the mower executes reel lift/lower actions, the VCU console logs raiseCutUnitSwitch state-change debug entries with timestamps. • Messages appear each time reels transition Up → Down or Down → Up. • No duplicate combined up/down messages appear for the same action. • Log entries include correct CAN timestamps.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create plan, Assign, begin execution of the plan., Verify all CutSwitchState change logs have both timestamp values<br>Expecct that there is no state gaps in CutSwitchState changes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2102</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-121 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213401"> VCU: Support Local Confirmation Timing Requirements (IRD128-2577) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:32:52 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-121</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371396</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: Support Local Confirmation Timing Requirements (IRD128-2577)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that the updated VCU firmware properly implements Local Confirmation Required (LCR) timing requirements using three VAI status messages and a minimum 400 ms delay before clearing LCR.<br> • Ensure that hazard and occlusion zone updates are fully received before LCR clears so the error does not re-trigger.<br> • Validate that updated LCR behavior is visible and traceable via VCU console output.<br><br>Scope:<br> • VCU firmware local confirmation logic.<br> • VAI-to-VCU sentinel status communication timing.<br> • Interaction between hazard, occlusion, and LCR state transitions.<br> • Testing requires a real mower; behavior cannot be accurately simulated.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • VCU firmware contains IRD128-2577 changes.<br> • VAI publishes sentinel status messages (rxSentinelStatus).<br> • DKS debug fields can be used to display status transitions in real time.<br> • Mobius Desktop provides access to DKS settings and VCU console output.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Real mower checked into Mobius.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client connected with access to VCU console.<br> • Hazard and occlusion zones capable of being triggered and cleared.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Real operating environment.<br> • VCU console visible.<br> • Local confirmation toggled via Auto/Manual switch.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Real mower with updated VCU firmware.<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Sentinel status messages printed with fields:<br>War, Haz, Occ, Sta<br> • Local confirmation state transitions.<br> • Timeout and message count thresholds.<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Local confirmation will not clear immediately after toggling into Auto.<br> • VCU waits for three consecutive sentinel messages and at least 400 ms before clearing LCR.<br> • Hazard and occlusion updates occur before LCR clears.<br> • VCU console prints continuous sentinel messages when debug settings are enabled.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Toggle mower to autonomous mode, Verify if at least 3 rxSentinelStatus log entries occur after clear grid succeded before local confirmation is cleared.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2103</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-122 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213402"> VCU: 30 Minute Idle Timeout Requires Local Confirmation (IRD128-2580) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:31:12 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-122</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371397</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: 30 Minute Idle Timeout Requires Local Confirmation (IRD128-2580)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br>• Verify that the 30 minute idle timeout now triggers a Local Confirmation Required (LCR) state.<br>• Confirm that after 30 minutes of inactivity, the mower no longer accepts missions until the operator performs local confirmation.<br>• Ensure the updated timeout behavior aligns with the new LCR flow implemented in prior IRD128 local confirmation work.<br><br>Scope:<br>• VCU idle-time monitoring logic.<br>• Integration between idle timeout and local confirmation state machine.<br>• Behavior requires real mower hardware (cannot be duplicated using simulation).<br><br>Assumptions:<br>• VCU firmware includes IRD128-2580 modifications linking idle timeout to LCR.<br>• Local confirmation toggling (Auto/Manual switch) is functioning correctly.<br>• Mobius can display mower readiness state and mission acceptance state.<br>• No hazard or occlusion errors interfere with baseline state before the idle timeout begins.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br>• Real mower powered on and checked into Mobius.<br>• Mower in a ready-to-command state with no active estops or errors.<br>• Local confirmation has already been satisfied prior to starting the idle timer.<br><br>Environment:<br>• Real mower in a safe idle location.<br>• No operator interaction during the 30-minute idle period.<br>• Mobius Desktop Client connected and monitoring mower state.<br><br>Equipment:<br>• Real mower with updated VCU firmware for IRD128-2580.<br>• Mobius Desktop Client.<br><br>Test Data:<br>• Idle timeout duration: 30 minutes.<br>• Local confirmation state transition after timeout.<br><br>Expected behavior:<br>• Mower begins in a state where missions can be accepted.<br>• After 30 minutes of continuous idle time, VCU triggers Local Confirmation Required.<br>• Mobius will show that the mower is no longer eligible to accept a mission.<br>• Operator must perform local confirmation before the mower can accept a new mission.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Power on VAK <br>Toggle mower to autonomous mode and wait, Verify LocalConfirmationTimeout @45 Seconds &amp;amp; LocalConfirmationTimeout 100 Seconds</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
