  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-123 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213403"> Mobius Client: Play/Pause Control Restricted to Assigned User (IRD128-2594) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:31:20 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-123</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371398</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius Client: Play/Pause Control Restricted to Assigned User (IRD128-2594)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br>• Verify that the Play/Start/Stop/Pause controls in Mobius are only available to the user who is assigned to the asset.<br>• Confirm that unassigned users cannot start, stop, or pause an asset even if they are logged in to the same server.<br>• Ensure that assigning an asset to a different user correctly transfers control permissions.<br><br>Scope:<br>• Mobius Desktop User Permissions Model.<br>• Asset assignment logic and UI control gating.<br>• Multi-user interactions on a shared Mobius server.<br><br>Assumptions:<br>• Mobius build contains IRD128-2594 permission enforcement changes.<br>• Both user accounts are authenticated and operating on the same server instance.<br>• Asset assignment behaves normally and updates in real time for users.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br>• Mobius Desktop Client running with two separate user accounts logged into the same server.<br>• At least one asset checked into Mobius and capable of running plans.<br>• Both users have visibility to the checked-in asset but only one user should initially have it assigned.<br><br>Environment:<br>• Mobius Desktop Client (multi-user environment).<br>• Shared Mobius Server hosting the assets and assignments.<br><br>Equipment:<br>• Mobius Desktop Client.<br>• At least one simulator or real mower checked in.<br><br>Test Data:<br>• Asset assignment states (User A assigned, then User B assigned).<br>• Start/Stop/Play/Pause UI controls.<br><br>Expected behavior:<br>• Only the user assigned to the asset can start, pause, or stop the asset.<br>• Unassigned users see the play/pause controls but interactions do nothing.<br>• When assignment is transferred, control permissions transfer as well.<br>• Users without assignment cannot override or interrupt another user's active mission.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create Plan, Assign, begin execution<br>Switch user amd pause<br>Click play<br>Switch user amd pause<br>Click play, Verify user can play the plan</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2107</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
