  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-124 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213404"> Mobius: Obstacle Intersection Validation for Loaded Plans (IRD128-2543) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:33:30 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-124</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371399</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Obstacle Intersection Validation for Loaded Plans (IRD128-2543)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that Mobius correctly validates plans when loading them, detecting intersections with obstacles or undrivable regions.<br> • Ensure that plans created under valid conditions fail to load when the map geometry is later modified (e.g., adding obstacles, shrinking fairways).<br> • Confirm that validation uses consistent planner parameters (e.g., PathEndExtension, swath type, intersection set values) so that a valid plan loads successfully when no changes have occurred.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Plan-loading validation logic within Mobius Client and Server.<br> • Intersections between planned paths, fairway geometry, and obstacles.<br> • Behavior when the map or planning parameters are modified after plan creation.<br> • Applicable to offline-created plans, imported plans, and plans stored in Mobius.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Mobius build includes IRD128-2543 planning-library fixes.<br> • Planning library correctly checks all plan segments for intersection violations.<br> • PathEndExtension parameters match between plan creation and plan validation.<br> • Plans retain necessary metadata (e.g., swath types, intersection sets) for proper validation.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Client and Server running with updated planning library (3.5 candidate or later).<br> • Simulator checked in and positioned near a fairway with an existing plan.<br> • Fairway plan previously generated under valid map conditions.<br> • Map editor enabled for obstacle creation and fairway editing.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client (Offline Planner and Map Editor available).<br> • Simulator (or mower) registered on the same server instance.<br> • Planning library DLLs updated with IRD128-2543 fixes.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Simulator or real mower (sim sufficient).<br> • Map containing a fairway with at least one saved plan.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • Original plan generated under valid geometry.<br> • Modified map including:<br> • New obstacle intersecting the fairway,<br> • Shrunk fairway boundary that causes the plan to intersect the undrivable region.<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Loading a plan without modifying the map should succeed with no errors.<br> • Adding an obstacle that intersects the plan path should cause plan load failure with:<br>"Plan intersects an undrivable region of the map."<br> • Shrinking or modifying the fairway such that the plan is no longer fully drivable should also cause the same validation failure.<br> • Plan validation should not produce discontinuity errors or mismatched parameters.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create Plan, Assign, Verify that Mobius correctly validates plans when loading them, detecting intersections with obstacles or undrivable regions.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2108</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-125 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5213405"> Mobius: Offline Planning: Support for AB (Guidance) Lines (IRD128-2354) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">12/17/2025 03:04:00 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">01/28/2026 04:31:13 AM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-125</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3371400</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Offline Planning: Support for AB (Guidance) Lines (IRD128-2354)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Objective:<br> • Verify that AB Lines (Guidance Lines) created in the Map Editor can be used within Offline Planning to generate a valid plan.<br> • Ensure that both straight AB lines (two-point lines) and curved multi-point guidance lines are selectable and function correctly during Swath Generation.<br> • Confirm that the planner correctly centers and orients swaths based on the selected guidance line.<br><br>Scope:<br> • Map Editor line-creation tools and guidance-line naming.<br> • Offline Planning Swath Generation logic using guidance lines.<br> • Support for both linear AB lines and curved guidance paths.<br> • Plan creation lifecycle within the Offline Planner.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client build includes IRD128-2354 functionality for guidance-line–based planning.<br> • Guidance Lines are properly stored as part of the map data and rendered in Offline Planning.<br> • Planner consumes guidance-line geometry to generate swaths without errors.<br> • Asset check-in is required for enabling the planning workflow.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 4.0</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client running and connected.<br> • At least one asset checked in to Mobius.<br> • Fairway available on the map.<br> • Ability to create and save Guidance Lines in the Map Editor.<br><br>Environment:<br> • Mobius Map Editor with line-creation tools enabled.<br> • Offline Planner with access to all guidance lines associated with the map.<br> • Swath Generation step visible and functional.<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Desktop Client.<br> • Simulator or physical mower checked in (sim sufficient).<br><br>Test Data:<br> • One straight AB Line created from exactly two points.<br> • One curved guidance line created from three or more points.<br><br>Expected behavior:<br> • Straight AB Line and multi-point curved guidance line appear in the Guidance Line dropdown during Swath Generation.<br> • Selecting a Guidance Line causes the planner to generate swaths oriented to that line.<br> • Both straight and curved guidance lines successfully produce usable plans.<br> • No planner validation errors occur due solely to the use of AB Lines.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create Plan using guidence lines, Assign, Verify that AB Lines (Guidance Lines) created in the Map Editor can be used within Offline Planning to generate a valid plan, by checking the Curvature.</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Passed</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"E39191" width=3D"80%">High</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">https://testlink.asirobots.com/linkto.php?tprojectPrefix=3DAG&amp;item=3Dtestcase&amp;id=3DAG-2109</td>
     </tr>
