  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-127 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5364615"> Mobius: Planner Objectives compare the continue point to the current location of the mower. (Verifies To Far From Start error) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/17/2026 06:17:23 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 10:17:15 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-127</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3459993</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mobius: Planner Objectives compare the continue point to the current location of the mower. (Verifies To Far From Start error)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Objective:<br> • Verifies when the mower is manually moved, the Mobius planner objectives compare the continue point to the current location of the mower. (Users should no longer get a To Far From Start Error Message)<br> <br> Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Path plans are created that connect the mowers current location to the continue point of a plan.<br> • Simulator is located withing the area coverage map shape.</p> <p>• Simulator is toggled to manual mode &gt;&gt; moved to a new location (teleport) &gt;&gt; then toggled back to Autonomous mode.&nbsp;<br> <br> Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL/HIL.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Mower Version 3.8</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"><p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Preconditions:<br> • Mobius app installed and running with latest version of "AreaCoverageLibraries" integrated<br> • Map is published in mobius.<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> <br> Environment:<br> • Map Loaded - SmallMowingMap.<br> <br> Equipment:<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build.</p> <p>• Latest Mobius Client and Server Build<br> <br> Test Data:<br> • Map.<br> • Teleport Location</p> <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: Create plan and assign<br>2: Pause Mower in Light bulb turn<br>3: Toggle to Manual Mode<br>4: Teleport to new Location more that 0.125m (5ft) away from continue point, Still an Active Assignment<br>5: Toggle back to Autonomous mode, Mobius to cancel the current assignment<br>6: Mobius will create a new assignment with the same objective using the offline planner, - New Assignment&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;- Same Objective&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;- Play and Resumed Mowing&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;- Users no longer get a To Far From Start message&amp;nbsp;</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Run Results:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automated:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Yes</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Automation Tool:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"$myLookupColor" width=3D"80%">TestPlatform</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Assigned:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Priority:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"FFFF66" width=3D"80%">Medium</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>External ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Legacy Keywords:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
    </tbody>
   </table> <br> <br>
  </div>
