  <div class=3D"Section1">
   <table class=3D"grid" cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" border=3D"0" width=3D"100%">
    <tbody>
     <tr>
      <td bgcolor=3D"f0f0f0" colspan=3D"2" valign=3D"top"><h3 class=3D"formtitle">LFWM2-VERTCA-131 <a href=3D"perspective.req?projectId=3D152&amp;docId=3D5482380"> VCU: SMU: WAT: Verify the number of expected Zones and Type (Hazard / Warning) </a>&nbsp; 
        <div class=3D"subText">
         Created: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 07:20:43 PM UTC</font> &nbsp;Updated: <font color=3D"336699">02/23/2026 07:20:43 PM UTC</font>
        </div></h3></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Project ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">LFWM2-VERTCA-131</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Global ID:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">GID-3477639</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: SMU: WAT: Verify the number of expected Zones and Type (Hazard / Warning)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">SMU =3D Saftey Management Unit<br>WAT =3D Walk Around Test<br><br>Objective:<br> • Verify Identified Violation Zones Exist<br> • Verify Identified Violation Zones Data Sates <br> • LFWM2-SubSys_Rqmt-24<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL/HIL with SMU and WAT</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius installed and running<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> • SetDKS to enable the WAT in setup steps<br><br>Environment:<br> • Initial VCU | SMU | WAT initialization<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Server - Up and running<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build with SMU and WAT.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • SetDKS value to enable<br> • Identified Holocom/DKS values that represent zones<br> • Identified Holocom/DKS values that represent Zone States (Complete / Not Complete)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: • SetDksValue Enabled • Start Mobius Server • Mower Checked in • Veriy VCU Zones, Expect WAT Zones &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect WAT Zones data states</td>
