     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Name:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">VCU: SMU: WAT: Verify incomplete zones block operations until completed in order (In sequence)</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">SMU =3D Saftey Management Unit<br>WAT =3D Walk Around Test<br><br>Objective:<br> • Verify incomplete zones block operations until completed in order (In sequence)<br> • LFWM2-SubSys_Rqmt-21<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL/HIL with SMU and WAT</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius installed and running<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> • SetDKS to enable the WAT in setup steps<br><br>Environment:<br> • Initial VCU | SMU | WAT initialization<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Server - Up and running<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build with SMU and WAT.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • SetDKS value to disabled<br> • Identified Holocom/DKS values that represent Zones<br> • Identified The expected start Zone and end Zone for correct order</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: • SetDksValue Enabled• Start Mobius Server • Mower Checked in • Veriy incomplete zones block operations, Expect Zone 1 Complete, Incomplete Zones 2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2 Complete, Incomplete Zones 3,4,5,6,7,8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3 Complete, Incomplete Zones 4,5,6,7,8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3,4 Complete, Incomplete Zones 5,6,7,8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3,4,5 Complete, Incomplete Zones 6,7,8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3,4,5,6 Complete, Incomplete Zones 7,8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3,4,5,6,7 Complete, Incomplete Zones 8,9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8 Complete, Incomplete Zones 9 &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Blocked<br>Expect Zone 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9 Complete, No Incomplete Zones &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Expect Operations Go</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Test Case Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Not Scheduled</td>
