      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">SMU =3D Saftey Management Unit<br>WAT =3D Walk Around Test<br><br>Objective:<br> • Verify a fault is triggered when zones are completed out of sequence (Out of sequence)<br> • LFWM2-SubSys_Rqmt-21<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of the VCU SIL/HIL with SMU and WAT</td>
