      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius installed and running<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> • SetDKS to enable the WAT in setup steps<br><br>Environment:<br> • Initial VCU | SMU | WAT initialization<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Server - Up and running<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build with SMU and WAT.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • SetDKS value to disabled<br> • Identified Holocom/DKS values that represent Zones<br> • Identified The expected start Zone and end Zone for correct order</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: • SetDksValue Enabled• Start Mobius Server • Mower Checked in • Veriy Zone(s) completed out of sequence triggers Expected fault, Expect Zone 2 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 3 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 4 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 5 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 6 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 7 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 8 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation<br>Expect Zone 9 Complete, Expect Fault State =3D Waiting for Implementation</td>
