      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius installed and running<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> • SetDKS to enable the WAT in setup steps<br><br>Environment:<br> • Initial VCU | SMU | WAT initialization<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Server - Up and running<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build with SMU and WAT.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • SetDKS value to disabled<br> • Identified Holocom/DKS values that represent the nuber of Zones<br> • Identified The expected start Zone and end Zone for correct order</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: • SetDksValue Enabled• Start Mobius Server • Mower Checked in • Complete WAT for all zones • Expect &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Mower can start Autonomous operations, &lt;p&gt;Expect &amp;gt;&amp;gt; All zones Passed &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Mower is able to start Autonomous Operation&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;Expect:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;ul&gt;<br> &lt;li&gt;<br> &lt;p&gt;Ensure that local confirmation occurs immediately after the WAT results have been validated&lt;/p&gt;<br> &lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;/ul&gt;</td>
     </tr>
