      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Status:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"" width=3D"80%">Draft</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">SMU =3D Saftey Management Unit<br>WAT =3D Walk Around Test<br><br>Objective:<br> • Verify telemetry signal or expected VCU state when invoked from Mobius<br> • LFWM2-SubSys_Rqmt-152<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of Mobius and the VCU SIL/HIL with SMU and WAT</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Scheduled Release:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%"></td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius installed and running<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> • SetDKS to enable the WAT in setup steps<br><br>Environment:<br> • Initial VCU | SMU | WAT initialization<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Server - Up and running<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build with SMU and WAT.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • SetDKS value to disabled<br> • Identified Telemetry value from Mobius &gt;to&gt; VCU when initiated with Mobius</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: • SetDksValue Enabled• Start Mobius Server • Mower Checked in • Initiate WAT with Mobius • Expect &amp;gt;&amp;gt; VCU state is informed, Expect &amp;gt;&amp;gt; VCU is informed</td>
     </tr>
