      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Setup:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">Preconditions:<br> • Mobius installed and running<br> • Vehicle is checked in and powered on.<br> • SetDKS to enable the WAT in setup steps<br><br>Environment:<br> • Initial VCU | SMU | WAT initialization<br><br>Equipment:<br> • Mobius Server - Up and running<br> • Latest SIL/VCU Build with SMU and WAT.<br><br>Test Data:<br> • SetDKS value to disabled<br> • Identified Telemetry value from VCU &gt;to&gt; Mobius of: <br> • The status of each validation zone during the test<br> • The status of whether or not the walk-around test is required</td>
     </tr>
     <tr bgcolor=3D"ffffff">
      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Steps:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">1: • SetDksValue Enabled• Start Mobius Server • Mower Checked in • Initiate WAT • Expect &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Mobius is informed of:<br> • The status of each validation zone during the test<br> • The status of whether or not the walk-around test is required, Expect &amp;gt;&amp;gt; Mobius is informed of: <br> • The status of each validation zone during the test<br> • The status of whether or not the walk-around test is required</td>
