      <td width=3D"20%"><b>Description:</b></td>
      <td bgcolor=3D"ffffff" width=3D"80%">**Descoped for Current Release**<br> SMU =3D Saftey Management Unit<br>WAT =3D Walk Around Test<br><br>Objective:<br> • Verify that each local set for each zone is sent to Mobius (UI/Message?)<br> • LFWM2-SubSys_Rqmt-25<br><br>Scope:<br> • Mobius is in control of the vehicle during the test.<br> • Applies to SIL and HIL.<br><br>Assumptions:<br> • Assumes the latest build of Mobius and the VCU SIL/HIL with SMU and WAT</td>
